WEBVTT

00:12.833 --> 00:15.333
<i>[boy] </i>♪ There once was a lord ♪

00:15.416 --> 00:17.291
<i>♪ In dark woods ♪</i>

00:17.375 --> 00:24.250
<i>♪ Wearing a strange silver band ♪</i>

00:24.916 --> 00:29.416
<i>♪ Around his hand ♪</i>

00:35.708 --> 00:37.416
<i>-[wheels rumble]</i>
<i>-[horse neighs]</i>

00:37.500 --> 00:42.125
<i>♪ The band was charmed</i>
<i>With ore from stars ♪</i>

00:42.208 --> 00:49.208
<i>♪ Bidding all monsters away ♪</i>

00:50.083 --> 00:53.958
<i>♪ Away ♪</i>

00:54.958 --> 00:59.000
<i>♪ On that quiet eve ♪</i>

00:59.583 --> 01:03.291
<i>♪ Among these trees ♪</i>

01:03.375 --> 01:08.208
<i>♪ A bandit slew the good lord ♪</i>

01:08.291 --> 01:11.250
<i>♪ Stealing that band ♪</i>

01:11.333 --> 01:15.833
<i>♪ Off a dead man's hand ♪</i>

01:17.250 --> 01:23.291
<i>♪ For the bandit also feared ♪</i>

01:23.875 --> 01:29.083
<i>♪ Monsters ♪</i>

01:29.166 --> 01:32.541
<i>Sugo, keep your eyes and ears open!</i>

01:33.208 --> 01:34.875
<i>It's frightening the girls.</i>

01:35.791 --> 01:37.791
<i>-[Sugo] They wouldn't even be scared…</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

01:37.875 --> 01:39.875
<i>…if you hadn't gotten lost.</i>

01:39.958 --> 01:42.625
<i>Really, Papa, you grew up in Kaedwen.</i>

01:42.708 --> 01:45.583
<i>King clearly dug new trails. [grunts]</i>

01:46.666 --> 01:48.250
<i>[girl] Is it true, Papa?</i>

01:48.333 --> 01:50.583
<i>Are bandits killing innocents</i>
<i>along these trails?</i>

01:50.666 --> 01:52.333
<i>[man] Oh, pumpkin.</i>

01:53.541 --> 01:55.875
<i>There are no bandits. [grunts]</i>

01:59.208 --> 02:01.208
<i>[girls screaming]</i>

02:03.208 --> 02:05.916
<i>[neighing frantically]</i>

02:11.083 --> 02:12.000
<i>No!</i>

02:13.125 --> 02:15.125
<i>[all screaming]</i>

02:16.708 --> 02:18.958
<i>-Sister!</i>
<i>-[limbs squelching]</i>

02:23.458 --> 02:25.250
<i>[panting]</i>

02:28.666 --> 02:30.250
<i>[sobbing]</i>

02:30.791 --> 02:31.708
<i>[gasping]</i>

02:34.041 --> 02:35.541
<i>[indistinct fluttering]</i>

02:35.625 --> 02:36.791
<i>[Sugo yelps]</i>

02:47.750 --> 02:49.041
<i>[Sugo] A witcher.</i>

02:55.708 --> 02:58.041
<i>-[ringing sound]</i>
<i>-[creaking]</i>

02:58.125 --> 03:00.458
<i>[witcher chuckles] Fancy look.</i>

03:01.625 --> 03:03.416
<i>[snarling]</i>

03:03.500 --> 03:05.666
<i>You must make a killing</i>
<i>at druid festivals.</i>

03:06.208 --> 03:08.541
<i>Don't usually see your sorts</i>
<i>around these parts.</i>

03:08.625 --> 03:10.208
<i>[screeches]</i>

03:14.083 --> 03:15.625
<i>-Ha! I see.</i>
<i>-[creature snarling]</i>

03:16.458 --> 03:19.416
<i>You're a trailblazer,</i>
<i>flaunting the new fad.</i>

03:19.500 --> 03:20.708
<i>Trendsetter, you.</i>

03:20.791 --> 03:22.833
<i>-[screeches]</i>
<i>-Very bold! [grunts]</i>

03:23.583 --> 03:26.333
<i>Whoa, there.</i>
<i>People should get acquainted more, really.</i>

03:26.416 --> 03:29.000
<i>[grunts] Converse, a little foreplay.</i>

03:29.708 --> 03:31.500
<i>Especially when</i>
<i>one's about to kill the other.</i>

03:32.583 --> 03:35.750
<i>Though you leshens don't speak,</i>
<i>so there's the rub.</i>

03:38.625 --> 03:39.458
<i>[screeches]</i>

04:01.416 --> 04:03.000
<i>[grunting]</i>

04:06.833 --> 04:10.333
<i>[grunts] Forest hobo</i>
<i>or deadly, flapping swarm.</i>

04:12.750 --> 04:14.333
<i>Let's pick a look… [grunts]</i>

04:15.041 --> 04:16.125
<i>…and stick with it.</i>

04:20.291 --> 04:22.125
<i>Deadly, flapping swarm it is.</i>

04:25.375 --> 04:26.208
<i>[grunts]</i>

04:37.208 --> 04:39.041
<i>Away. It's not dead.</i>

04:39.125 --> 04:41.500
<i>So kill it. You're a witcher.</i>

04:41.583 --> 04:43.750
<i>There are several ways to kill a leshen.</i>

04:43.833 --> 04:46.041
<i>Behead it,</i>
<i>sacrifice a few of its furry pets,</i>

04:46.750 --> 04:48.875
<i>even a few old dryad spells will do.</i>

04:49.750 --> 04:51.166
<i>Which will you…</i>

04:53.291 --> 04:54.875
<i>[growls]</i>

04:54.958 --> 04:55.791
<i>[screeches]</i>

05:07.208 --> 05:11.708
<i>[leshen] </i>Garean bhaedh aip me vhoelynath.

05:12.916 --> 05:17.958
<i>Garean bhaedh aip me vhoelynath.</i>

05:20.333 --> 05:22.708
<i>Thought you said they don't speak?</i>

05:23.750 --> 05:27.416
<i>[hissing whisper] </i>Garean bhaedh
aip me vhoelynath.

05:28.916 --> 05:29.958
<i>They don't.</i>

05:31.958 --> 05:33.958
<i>[dramatic theme music playing]</i>

05:39.416 --> 05:41.000
<i>[trinkets rustling]</i>

05:49.166 --> 05:50.000
<i>Wait!</i>

05:50.083 --> 05:52.083
<i>Wait. I'm noble blood.</i>

05:52.166 --> 05:53.583
<i>You can't leave me here.</i>

05:54.166 --> 05:55.208
<i>What am I to do?</i>

05:59.791 --> 06:02.375
<i>He said, "Practice your sad face,</i>

06:02.458 --> 06:05.375
<i>and maybe</i>
<i>a passerby will offer you a ride."</i>

06:06.208 --> 06:07.875
<i>[woman] And what of your sisters?</i>

06:09.208 --> 06:12.583
<i>The witcher said</i>
<i>to use my sad face on the alderman too.</i>

06:13.208 --> 06:14.916
<i>So he'd spare some men to…</i>

06:15.625 --> 06:16.916
<i>gather the bodies.</i>

06:24.375 --> 06:25.541
<i>Dry eyes, child.</i>

06:26.791 --> 06:31.083
<i>I'll see that your father and sisters are</i>
<i>returned to you and laid to rest properly.</i>

06:33.208 --> 06:35.833
<i>[woman] Sugo's father was</i>
<i>a treasured member of the Assembly</i>

06:35.916 --> 06:37.708
<i>and a loyal subject to our king.</i>

06:37.791 --> 06:40.750
<i>My students and I resubmit our petition.</i>

06:41.333 --> 06:43.708
<i>Seize the witcher home of Kaer Morhen</i>

06:43.791 --> 06:47.291
<i>and exile its occupants</i>
<i>for crimes against Kaedwen's people.</i>

06:47.791 --> 06:50.666
<i>From what the boy told us, Your Highness,</i>

06:50.750 --> 06:54.791
<i>the witcher slew the leshen</i>
<i>that was terrorizing our forests.</i>

06:54.875 --> 06:58.666
<i>Lady Zerbst, since when</i>
<i>have leshens prowled about Kaedwen,</i>

06:58.750 --> 07:00.666
<i>never mind with such hostility?</i>

07:01.333 --> 07:02.458
<i>Eh?</i>

07:02.541 --> 07:07.083
<i>Oh, you're suggesting the witchers</i>
<i>have been staging these forest attacks.</i>

07:07.166 --> 07:10.458
<i>So scandalous, Madam Gilcrest.</i>

07:10.541 --> 07:13.666
<i>Monster species have dwindled</i>
<i>under their swords.</i>

07:13.750 --> 07:15.708
<i>-[murmuring]</i>
<i>-They need coin.</i>

07:15.791 --> 07:18.750
<i>Some have turned to mercenary work,</i>
<i>others criminality.</i>

07:18.833 --> 07:21.916
<i>One even took a bounty</i>
<i>on a cheating husband's head.</i>

07:22.000 --> 07:24.583
<i>And you have evidence</i>
<i>to prove your conspiracy?</i>

07:24.666 --> 07:29.041
<i>Or are we to merely bank</i>
<i>on your magical intuition?</i>

07:29.125 --> 07:31.083
<i>It's their natures, my lady.</i>

07:32.583 --> 07:35.375
<i>Witchers are the offspring</i>
<i>of foul sorcery.</i>

07:35.875 --> 07:37.125
<i>Roaming our lands,</i>

07:37.208 --> 07:39.583
<i>voting themselves the stalkers of evil,</i>

07:39.666 --> 07:41.625
<i>extorting coin from the gullible.</i>

07:42.125 --> 07:46.791
<i>Honest, simple peasants who ascribe</i>
<i>all misfortune to spells and monsters.</i>

07:46.875 --> 07:48.833
<i>Mages create the witcher.</i>

07:48.916 --> 07:52.583
<i>Then presume it's our duty to hold</i>
<i>the bucket and mop up their brown mess.</i>

07:52.666 --> 07:54.208
<i>[attendants laughing]</i>

07:55.416 --> 07:56.583
<i>[king chuckles]</i>

07:57.333 --> 07:59.458
<i>I'm with Lady Zerbst on this one.</i>

07:59.958 --> 08:02.041
<i>The witchers remain at Kaer Morhen.</i>

08:02.125 --> 08:04.958
<i>At least until such time</i>
<i>as evidence is provided</i>

08:06.250 --> 08:08.000
<i>that supports your theory.</i>

08:09.875 --> 08:11.875
<i>[attendants murmuring]</i>

08:23.333 --> 08:25.333
<i>[upbeat folk music playing]</i>

08:26.875 --> 08:29.625
<i>When a witcher inflicts pain,</i>

08:29.708 --> 08:32.458
<i>he experiences ecstasy.</i>

08:33.250 --> 08:35.625
<i>[hooded figure]</i>
<i>The creature's words are Ellyon.</i>

08:35.708 --> 08:38.916
<i>A dead elven dialect</i>
<i>linked to darker times.</i>

08:39.000 --> 08:41.416
<i>Few remember the ancient tongue.</i>
<i>Fewer dare speak it.</i>

08:42.333 --> 08:44.583
<i>But how a leshen would know it</i>

08:44.666 --> 08:47.000
<i>or be afraid of some den--</i>

08:47.083 --> 08:48.583
<i>Never said it was afraid.</i>

08:49.333 --> 08:51.625
<i>You speak Ellyon, don't you, Filavandrel?</i>

08:52.375 --> 08:54.625
<i>You witchers are desperate for coin.</i>

08:55.208 --> 08:57.666
<i>Turning to elves for leads on work.</i>

08:58.833 --> 09:03.041
<i>These pleasures do not pay for themselves.</i>
<i>What did the leshen say?</i>

09:03.708 --> 09:05.541
<i>"Beware the den of my dead."</i>

09:05.625 --> 09:08.500
<i>Hmm. Things you don't wish</i>
<i>to hear in a bath.</i>

09:09.875 --> 09:12.750
<i>Did you notice anything else unusual?</i>

09:13.250 --> 09:15.000
<i>There was an energy in the woods.</i>

09:15.750 --> 09:17.375
<i>Some sort of magic, maybe.</i>

09:17.458 --> 09:19.416
<i>Controlling the leshen, bewitching it.</i>

09:20.166 --> 09:21.208
<i>What's your face?</i>

09:22.416 --> 09:24.041
<i>Over the last four summers,</i>

09:24.833 --> 09:26.916
<i>girls have been disappearing</i>
<i>from our ranks.</i>

09:27.000 --> 09:29.041
<i>Oh, God, no elf drama.</i>

09:29.625 --> 09:33.250
<i>[Filavandrel] The first we feared were</i>
<i>deserting us after the last cleansing.</i>

09:33.750 --> 09:38.250
<i>-But the disappearances haven't stopped.</i>
<i>-Tragic, really. Very terrible.</i>

09:38.333 --> 09:41.583
<i>One of the first to vanish</i>
<i>was a young mage, Kitsu.</i>

09:42.750 --> 09:45.875
<i>She spoke Ellyon.</i>
<i>We should return to these forests.</i>

09:46.708 --> 09:48.541
<i>See, I'm a monster hunter, Fil,</i>

09:48.625 --> 09:51.958
<i>not an elf wrangler, not even</i>
<i>the murderous ones, but good luck.</i>

09:52.041 --> 09:54.083
<i>[Filavandrel] A favor to a friend, then?</i>

09:54.750 --> 09:57.375
<i>[witcher] Favors and friends</i>
<i>don't pay bills.</i>

09:57.458 --> 09:58.666
<i>Quite the opposite.</i>

09:59.166 --> 10:01.041
<i>[Filavandrel] You've really no shame.</i>

10:01.125 --> 10:04.916
<i>I have a reputation and</i>
<i>a healthy estimation of my talent's worth.</i>

10:05.875 --> 10:10.166
<i>My apologies for trying to save you</i>
<i>from a wasted winter at Kaer Morhen.</i>

10:10.250 --> 10:12.541
<i>[laughs] Wasted?</i>

10:13.041 --> 10:15.791
<i>Well, there's drinking, eating, sleeping.</i>

10:16.291 --> 10:17.166
<i>All free.</i>

10:17.250 --> 10:21.291
<i>[Filavandrel] And the training</i>
<i>of another greedy gang of young witchers.</i>

10:22.000 --> 10:23.500
<i>I leave that to my peers.</i>

10:24.041 --> 10:25.000
<i>[Filavandrel sighs]</i>

10:25.083 --> 10:30.708
<i>Imagine if you witchers labored</i>
<i>for more than just thrill and coin.</i>

10:31.458 --> 10:33.958
<i>Imagine if you elves wielded your swords</i>

10:34.041 --> 10:36.166
<i>-as well as you do guilt.</i>
<i>-[cloak rustling]</i>

10:46.166 --> 10:47.416
<i>[woman] Please! Get them!</i>

10:47.500 --> 10:48.333
<i>[dog barking]</i>

10:48.416 --> 10:50.291
<i>[man] Vesemir, get over here!</i>

10:50.375 --> 10:53.291
<i>[woman muttering incoherently] Where do…</i>
<i>Hey! They must go!</i>

10:53.375 --> 10:55.041
<i>[wailing and giggling]</i>

10:56.166 --> 10:57.916
<i>Now they're nibbling. No! [giggles]</i>

10:58.000 --> 10:59.791
<i>Licking. Ooh! They're licking.</i>

11:00.416 --> 11:02.500
<i>-[laughing] Oh! Tongues!</i>
<i>-[men grunting]</i>

11:04.125 --> 11:06.291
<i>-[woman] No! Aah!</i>
<i>-Vesemir!</i>

11:06.375 --> 11:08.416
<i>I told you, double knots!</i>

11:08.500 --> 11:10.625
<i>-I did, Father. Just as you showed.</i>
<i>-[woman wailing]</i>

11:10.708 --> 11:13.166
<i>Let's see if the boy can handle</i>
<i>fetching a wet cloth.</i>

11:13.750 --> 11:15.250
<i>[woman screams]</i>

11:16.041 --> 11:18.750
<i>A lesser man</i>
<i>would sell your boy to another family.</i>

11:18.833 --> 11:19.833
<i>[man] Yes, sir.</i>

11:19.916 --> 11:24.000
<i>At least my son proves a measure</i>
<i>of your generous character.</i>

11:24.083 --> 11:27.458
<i>Head to the market.</i>
<i>We will need blue gum to sedate our lady.</i>

11:27.541 --> 11:29.416
<i>-[woman] No!</i>
<i>-Try not to cock it up.</i>

11:29.500 --> 11:31.458
<i>[woman cackling madly]</i>

11:31.541 --> 11:33.583
<i>Please stop! Please make it stop!</i>

11:33.666 --> 11:34.625
<i>-[man] No.</i>
<i>-[woman] No!</i>

11:35.666 --> 11:38.416
<i>-[birds chirping]</i>
<i>-[horse neighing]</i>

11:43.625 --> 11:45.666
<i>Stop fidgeting!</i>

11:52.166 --> 11:54.291
<i>-[giggles]</i>
<i>-[slap]</i>

11:54.375 --> 11:55.708
<i>[neighs]</i>

11:55.791 --> 11:57.458
<i>[grunts] Aah! Oh!</i>

12:01.166 --> 12:02.125
<i>Oh!</i>

12:03.333 --> 12:04.875
<i>[laughing]</i>

12:05.583 --> 12:08.708
<i>Poor Illyana.</i>
<i>I didn't even have to take a shot.</i>

12:08.791 --> 12:11.625
<i>Moron! You could've killed me.</i>

12:12.541 --> 12:13.625
<i>Here to bother me?</i>

12:13.708 --> 12:16.250
<i>The Lord insisted</i>
<i>I look after you in the market.</i>

12:16.333 --> 12:18.291
<i>Seemed rather pissed.</i>

12:18.375 --> 12:19.791
<i>[Vesemir sighs]</i>

12:19.875 --> 12:22.583
<i>We slave away all day long,</i>
<i>getting shout at,</i>

12:22.666 --> 12:26.291
<i>and the only coin we get</i>
<i>is when we're sent to fetch them goods.</i>

12:26.375 --> 12:29.958
<i>Just be happy you have a roof over</i>
<i>your head and your belly's not empty.</i>

12:30.041 --> 12:34.541
<i>Barely a roof, barely not empty.</i>
<i>Just enough to keep us here breathing.</i>

12:35.708 --> 12:37.250
<i>-[horse whines]</i>
<i>-[Illyana] Fine.</i>

12:37.333 --> 12:38.625
<i>There's the world.</i>

12:38.708 --> 12:41.083
<i>What would you buy</i>
<i>if you had all its coin?</i>

12:41.166 --> 12:44.125
<i>I would get the hell out of this village</i>
<i>and travel the continent.</i>

12:44.208 --> 12:45.958
<i>-Adventure?</i>
<i>-Of course.</i>

12:46.041 --> 12:47.791
<i>-Glory?</i>
<i>-Oh, yes!</i>

12:47.875 --> 12:48.833
<i>Girls?</i>

12:49.875 --> 12:51.000
<i>[giggles]</i>

12:51.500 --> 12:53.833
<i>I'd buy a gorgeous lake house.</i>

12:54.333 --> 12:58.916
<i>My handsome husband and I would picnic</i>
<i>and drink wine by the water</i>

12:59.000 --> 13:01.333
<i>as our children played jacks nearby.</i>

13:01.416 --> 13:03.500
<i>You know what we should do?</i>

13:04.166 --> 13:06.500
<i>We should take this coin</i>
<i>and buy honey cake.</i>

13:06.583 --> 13:08.750
<i>And how will our lady get her herbs?</i>

13:10.416 --> 13:12.750
<i>-[man] Yes, three more of those.</i>
<i>-[woman] Fresh mixed grills!</i>

13:12.833 --> 13:14.333
<i>[man] There you are, sir.</i>

13:14.416 --> 13:16.166
<i>Stop! Thief!</i>

13:17.208 --> 13:18.791
<i>-Hey!</i>
<i>-[child laughs]</i>

13:19.291 --> 13:20.333
<i>This way!</i>

13:21.458 --> 13:22.958
<i>[panting]</i>

13:24.375 --> 13:25.666
<i>-Oh!</i>
<i>-[woman] Stop him!</i>

13:28.208 --> 13:29.625
<i>[upbeat music playing]</i>

13:38.500 --> 13:39.833
<i>[growls] Nutcase.</i>

13:53.041 --> 13:54.125
<i>Mmm!</i>

13:55.166 --> 13:56.750
<i>Save some for me!</i>

13:58.041 --> 14:00.666
<i>See, it worked. [chuckles]</i>

14:00.750 --> 14:01.916
<i>I knew it would.</i>

14:02.000 --> 14:04.250
<i>[Illyana laughs]</i>

14:08.708 --> 14:10.166
<i>[man] In Nilfgaard,</i>

14:10.250 --> 14:12.958
<i>they'd cut your thieving hands right off.</i>

14:14.000 --> 14:16.625
<i>Make you wear 'em</i>
<i>round your neck for weeks.</i>

14:17.958 --> 14:19.333
<i>Smart trick.</i>

14:20.166 --> 14:21.583
<i>Odd loot.</i>

14:21.666 --> 14:22.833
<i>Who you got who's sick?</i>

14:24.333 --> 14:25.916
<i>[chuckles]</i>

14:26.000 --> 14:26.833
<i>Where…</i>

14:26.916 --> 14:31.333
<i>Where'd a girl find balls like that</i>
<i>in an alley wi' a man like me?</i>

14:31.416 --> 14:35.500
<i>I steal them from smelly cowards</i>
<i>who try to bully young ladies.</i>

14:36.333 --> 14:37.541
<i>[belches]</i>

14:39.333 --> 14:40.333
<i>Who are you?</i>

14:40.416 --> 14:45.333
<i>A humanitarian, whose well-meaning ears</i>
<i>have heard of a local lady</i>

14:45.416 --> 14:48.291
<i>-lost to madness and fever…</i>
<i>-[gags]</i>

14:48.375 --> 14:50.708
<i>…seeing horrors that aren't really there.</i>

14:51.208 --> 14:55.166
<i>That blue gum will</i>
<i>certainly ease the affliction, but, uh…</i>

14:55.791 --> 14:57.250
<i>a sword would kill it.</i>

14:57.333 --> 14:58.375
<i>Name's Deglan.</i>

14:59.083 --> 15:01.333
<i>And you're gonna take me</i>
<i>to your noblewoman.</i>

15:01.833 --> 15:04.958
<i>Or I'm taking you two pests</i>
<i>back to the market.</i>

15:07.958 --> 15:09.458
<i>[woman groaning]</i>

15:11.916 --> 15:14.000
<i>[Deglan] A demon plagues this woman.</i>

15:14.083 --> 15:15.000
<i>A mahr.</i>

15:15.500 --> 15:19.208
<i>Puts you down with horrid delusions</i>
<i>and feeds off your madness.</i>

15:19.291 --> 15:21.750
<i>Meteorite ore disrupts the demon's magic,</i>

15:21.833 --> 15:23.833
<i>so it can be… removed.</i>

15:24.333 --> 15:25.958
<i>Out. Now. All of you.</i>

15:28.250 --> 15:29.416
<i>I'd like to remain.</i>

15:30.625 --> 15:34.041
<i>Your boy's likely seen</i>
<i>a monster or two in his time, no?</i>

15:34.541 --> 15:36.208
<i>[woman moaning]</i>

15:37.500 --> 15:39.583
<i>-Oof!</i>
<i>-[Deglan] I'll be casting the spell.</i>

15:39.666 --> 15:41.958
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-It's on you to catch the critter.</i>

15:43.166 --> 15:46.583
<i>But I thought a witcher slays monsters?</i>

15:46.666 --> 15:48.375
<i>[Deglan] To slay a beast,</i>

15:48.458 --> 15:50.416
<i>you've first got to understand it.</i>

15:50.500 --> 15:51.958
<i>-[woman groaning]</i>
<i>-Study it.</i>

15:52.458 --> 15:53.958
<i>Find its weakness.</i>

15:54.500 --> 15:56.750
<i>I want this sucker alive and kicking.</i>

15:57.875 --> 15:58.750
<i>If possible.</i>

15:59.333 --> 16:01.166
<i>[whispering in Elder Tongue]</i>

16:04.875 --> 16:07.375
<i>[groans and screams]</i>

16:09.708 --> 16:10.791
<i>Steady, young fella.</i>

16:10.875 --> 16:11.958
<i>Uh…</i>

16:13.208 --> 16:14.875
<i>[screeches]</i>

16:22.541 --> 16:23.708
<i>[squeals]</i>

16:25.541 --> 16:26.375
<i>[groans]</i>

16:30.833 --> 16:32.541
<i>-[groans]</i>
<i>-[creature hisses]</i>

16:32.625 --> 16:34.500
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[Deglan chuckles]</i>

16:35.083 --> 16:36.708
<i>And he asked to stay.</i>

16:38.000 --> 16:39.291
<i>[creature screeching]</i>

16:42.666 --> 16:44.375
<i>-[screeches]</i>
<i>-[yells]</i>

16:58.833 --> 17:01.083
<i>[Deglan] Never let 'em get in your head.</i>

17:01.666 --> 17:03.125
<i>Better dead than fled.</i>

17:06.875 --> 17:09.041
<i>There'll always be another monster.</i>

17:14.000 --> 17:15.000
<i>[woman] Vesemir.</i>

17:15.500 --> 17:17.000
<i>Fetch warm water.</i>

17:17.708 --> 17:18.791
<i>My head…</i>

17:18.875 --> 17:21.291
<i>Oh, my head hurts wildly.</i>

17:33.041 --> 17:34.458
<i>[coins jingling]</i>

17:34.541 --> 17:36.000
<i>Nice weight, isn't it?</i>

17:36.083 --> 17:39.291
<i>How much you suppose</i>
<i>the job cost that prick master of yours?</i>

17:40.875 --> 17:43.083
<i>Fear and ignorance are good business.</i>

17:44.416 --> 17:46.000
<i>For your service, young fella.</i>

17:54.416 --> 17:55.500
<i>Take me with you.</i>

17:56.666 --> 17:58.666
<i>Not many boys seek to be witchers.</i>

17:58.750 --> 18:02.083
<i>Even fewer seek a life</i>
<i>of fetching bedpans and water.</i>

18:02.166 --> 18:03.000
<i>And the girl?</i>

18:04.000 --> 18:05.291
<i>Your blue-eyed lass?</i>

18:06.583 --> 18:09.333
<i>You hesitated back with the mahr too.</i>

18:09.416 --> 18:13.000
<i>Witchers do not hesitate.</i>

18:22.666 --> 18:24.666
<i>[contemplative music playing]</i>

18:40.916 --> 18:43.250
<i>-Stop!</i>
<i>-Are you going to enjoy the day?</i>

18:43.333 --> 18:47.083
<i>Or are you still too shook</i>
<i>from your daring night of monster-slaying?</i>

18:47.166 --> 18:49.166
<i>It was your first time, Vesemir.</i>

18:49.750 --> 18:53.208
<i>Excuse me for wanting to be good</i>
<i>at something other than serving.</i>

18:53.291 --> 18:55.541
<i>Oh, I can see it now.</i>

18:55.625 --> 18:57.875
<i>You, adorned in battle armor,</i>

18:57.958 --> 18:59.583
<i>steel and silver swords,</i>

18:59.666 --> 19:03.541
<i>saving the continent from kikamores,</i>
<i>ghouls, and mad sorcerers.</i>

19:03.625 --> 19:05.291
<i>Evil would tremble.</i>

19:06.500 --> 19:09.916
<i>-Stylish armor, by the way.</i>
<i>-Imagine it however you like.</i>

19:10.666 --> 19:14.416
<i>Only way people like us survive is</i>
<i>to dream of ourselves as something else.</i>

19:15.000 --> 19:19.291
<i>Who knows? Perhaps someday</i>
<i>I'll be a princess who commands the snow.</i>

19:22.333 --> 19:23.333
<i>Uh!</i>

19:24.166 --> 19:25.041
<i>[Illyana giggles]</i>

19:25.708 --> 19:27.875
<i>Vesemir, I was only jesting.</i>

19:27.958 --> 19:29.458
<i>You find our fates funny?</i>

19:30.083 --> 19:34.250
<i>Why should I be meek and penniless</i>
<i>like my father? Or you like your mother?</i>

19:34.875 --> 19:37.750
<i>-What's got you so silly?</i>
<i>-You wouldn't understand.</i>

19:37.833 --> 19:40.125
<i>Vesemir, out there, we're nothing.</i>

19:40.791 --> 19:41.916
<i>Less than nothing.</i>

19:42.458 --> 19:45.000
<i>At least here,</i>
<i>at the estate, we have station.</i>

19:45.083 --> 19:46.750
<i>And if I could take care of you?</i>

19:47.333 --> 19:49.791
<i>The coin that witcher made last night,</i>

19:49.875 --> 19:51.416
<i>you should've saw it.</i>

19:51.916 --> 19:54.791
<i>I'd get you your lake house,</i>
<i>all your wine.</i>

19:54.875 --> 19:57.416
<i>Anything and everything.</i>

19:57.500 --> 19:58.458
<i>Yours.</i>

19:59.416 --> 20:01.583
<i>So trade my debt to a master I hate</i>

20:02.166 --> 20:04.083
<i>with a debt to one that I love?</i>

20:06.666 --> 20:08.708
<i>Wait, Illyana! Stay!</i>

20:09.208 --> 20:10.333
<i>You stay.</i>

20:22.083 --> 20:23.375
<i>[door opens]</i>

20:26.958 --> 20:28.500
<i>[man groaning]</i>

20:30.041 --> 20:30.958
<i>[sighs]</i>

20:41.666 --> 20:43.916
<i>[mutters]</i>

20:48.041 --> 20:49.500
<i>-[sighs]</i>
<i>-[receding footsteps]</i>

21:04.708 --> 21:06.708
<i>[contemplative music continues]</i>

21:18.708 --> 21:20.708
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

21:42.291 --> 21:43.916
<i>Lord Vesemir,</i>

21:44.000 --> 21:45.291
<i>my new best friend.</i>

21:45.375 --> 21:47.416
<i>Crossed a leshen on my way here.</i>

21:47.500 --> 21:48.416
<i>So we've heard.</i>

21:49.000 --> 21:51.250
<i>Meanwhile, I barely made enough this year</i>

21:51.333 --> 21:53.791
<i>to score a night</i>
<i>with a limp-pricked man-whore.</i>

21:53.875 --> 21:55.541
<i>Your woes break me, Luka.</i>

21:56.041 --> 21:59.041
<i>[Luka] Then we've got Sven here</i>
<i>bringing back new recruits.</i>

21:59.125 --> 22:01.541
<i>Bad enough</i>
<i>we're putting ourselves out of business</i>

22:01.625 --> 22:03.416
<i>with every monster we kill.</i>

22:03.500 --> 22:05.708
<i>Now there'll be even more of us.</i>

22:05.791 --> 22:09.750
<i>[grunts] Not my fault</i>
<i>people make more kids than coin.</i>

22:09.833 --> 22:12.166
<i>Also, short a man-whore?</i>

22:12.708 --> 22:14.125
<i>Go fuck yourself.</i>

22:14.208 --> 22:15.916
<i>Aren't you "short" everything?</i>

22:16.000 --> 22:19.291
<i>Boys,</i>
<i>monsters will fuck through the winter,</i>

22:19.375 --> 22:22.208
<i>then come spring,</i>
<i>there'll be jobs from here to Nazair.</i>

22:22.291 --> 22:24.666
<i>Until then, I say we perk up,</i>

22:24.750 --> 22:25.666
<i>drink up,</i>

22:26.166 --> 22:30.041
<i>and you two focus on breaking these brats</i>
<i>into the world of witchering.</i>

22:33.875 --> 22:36.500
<i>[Vesemir] "Witchers are rogues</i>
<i>without virtue."</i>

22:36.583 --> 22:39.666
<i>"True diabolical creatures,</i>
<i>fit only for killing."</i>

22:41.416 --> 22:44.250
<i>"There is no place</i>
<i>amidst honest men for them."</i>

22:45.250 --> 22:47.750
<i>My, my. How do you find this rubbish?</i>

22:47.833 --> 22:51.583
<i>A few of the boys spotted 'em</i>
<i>posted about towns on their way back.</i>

22:51.666 --> 22:54.500
<i>"Tetra Gilcrest." Sounds like a botanist.</i>

22:55.208 --> 22:56.166
<i>[Deglan] A purist.</i>

22:56.666 --> 23:00.583
<i>Rambles about being a descendant</i>
<i>of the first human mage.</i>

23:00.666 --> 23:03.166
<i>Would it have vexed you</i>
<i>to bury that lad's sisters?</i>

23:04.208 --> 23:06.833
<i>You're feeding fodder</i>
<i>to arses like Gilcrest.</i>

23:08.125 --> 23:10.166
<i>That's a wyvern tooth, not a basilisk.</i>

23:10.250 --> 23:11.958
<i>I'll mix and match as I please.</i>

23:12.583 --> 23:13.416
<i>[Vesemir] Look.</i>

23:14.125 --> 23:17.125
<i>-You know me and children.</i>
<i>-Get over it, young fella.</i>

23:17.208 --> 23:19.583
<i>'Cause you're teaching fencing</i>
<i>to the recruits.</i>

23:19.666 --> 23:23.333
<i>-[Vesemir] Am I being punished?</i>
<i>-I'm down two dozen witchers this winter.</i>

23:23.958 --> 23:28.083
<i>Wimps found employ</i>
<i>in other more lucrative nonsense.</i>

23:28.583 --> 23:30.791
<i>So we'll all be slogging more weight.</i>

23:30.875 --> 23:34.125
<i>A wonderful winter</i>
<i>of abandoned little tragedies.</i>

23:34.208 --> 23:35.041
<i>Lovely.</i>

23:35.125 --> 23:37.416
<i>[Deglan] Now, this leshen.</i>

23:38.500 --> 23:40.875
<i>Tell me you've considered</i>
<i>the thing was bewitched.</i>

23:40.958 --> 23:42.916
<i>[scoffs] I'm not a dullard.</i>

23:43.000 --> 23:45.333
<i>A croon could pull that feat.</i>

23:45.416 --> 23:47.416
<i>A higher vampire, definitely.</i>

23:48.208 --> 23:51.083
<i>Or it could be a new breed of leshen.</i>

23:51.166 --> 23:54.875
<i>Actually, just elves airing</i>
<i>their usual dirty trousers of victimhood.</i>

23:55.375 --> 23:56.958
<i>[Deglan scoffs] Shame.</i>

23:58.166 --> 24:01.250
<i>A few new beasts would be…</i>
<i>good for business.</i>

24:06.083 --> 24:08.208
<i>[man 1] Why'd the witcher not handle this?</i>

24:08.291 --> 24:11.416
<i>-[man 2] Lies and conspiracy.</i>
<i>-[woman 1] Look away from the faces.</i>

24:11.500 --> 24:12.333
<i>[flies buzzing]</i>

24:12.416 --> 24:14.791
<i>[woman 2] I'd heard</i>
<i>the leshen'd been killed.</i>

24:18.291 --> 24:22.208
<i>[Tetra] A whiff of basilisk breath</i>
<i>could snuff out ten strong men.</i>

24:23.625 --> 24:26.041
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Did you find</i>
<i>the creature's body?</i>

24:27.500 --> 24:30.291
<i>A witcher would need proof</i>
<i>to collect his coin.</i>

24:30.958 --> 24:32.458
<i>And yet…</i>

24:32.541 --> 24:34.166
<i>At least help me persuade the king</i>

24:34.250 --> 24:36.958
<i>to send an envoy</i>
<i>to Kaer Morhen to investigate, please.</i>

24:37.791 --> 24:41.458
<i>Your acolytes have played</i>
<i>to people's fears well enough.</i>

24:41.541 --> 24:44.250
<i>The mere act of sending an envoy</i>
<i>would indict the witchers,</i>

24:44.333 --> 24:45.916
<i>whatever the truth.</i>

24:46.708 --> 24:48.875
<i>Do you know</i>
<i>what's involved in making a witcher?</i>

24:50.041 --> 24:52.125
<i>The horrors done to their recruits?</i>

24:52.208 --> 24:54.958
<i>-Boys no older than your orphans here.</i>
<i>-[children laughing]</i>

24:55.916 --> 24:58.416
<i>Your late husband</i>
<i>would've understood this.</i>

24:58.916 --> 25:01.250
<i>I was an ardent admirer of Lord Zerbst.</i>

25:02.666 --> 25:04.000
<i>He was open-minded.</i>

25:04.791 --> 25:05.791
<i>Forward-thinking.</i>

25:06.541 --> 25:08.291
<i>Married you, after all.</i>

25:08.375 --> 25:10.541
<i>Careful, Tetra.</i>

25:11.041 --> 25:12.291
<i>Or be quiet.</i>

25:12.875 --> 25:16.083
<i>Kaedwen's laws grant a widow</i>
<i>her husband's seat at court.</i>

25:16.166 --> 25:18.791
<i>The laws say nothing</i>
<i>about erasing what she once was.</i>

25:19.791 --> 25:21.750
<i>Well, how fortunate, my lady,</i>

25:21.833 --> 25:24.208
<i>that few have wished to press the issue.</i>

25:25.291 --> 25:27.291
<i>[children grunting]</i>

25:42.791 --> 25:44.458
<i>You ain't fed us in days!</i>

25:44.541 --> 25:47.208
<i>We ain't given sleep, can barely stand up.</i>

25:47.708 --> 25:49.833
<i>Now you got us playing with swords?</i>

25:51.041 --> 25:53.958
<i>I don't wish to be here</i>
<i>any more than you do.</i>

25:54.833 --> 25:56.041
<i>I'll hazard a guess.</i>

25:56.125 --> 25:59.583
<i>You all imagine there are better fates</i>
<i>for you out there in the world.</i>

26:00.541 --> 26:02.666
<i>But out there, you have nothing.</i>

26:03.875 --> 26:05.916
<i>But here, we offer strength.</i>

26:06.000 --> 26:07.750
<i>-[boy grunts]</i>
<i>-Purpose.</i>

26:07.833 --> 26:08.875
<i>[yells]</i>

26:09.750 --> 26:10.625
<i>Respect.</i>

26:11.125 --> 26:13.958
<i>A chance at surviving</i>
<i>the very horrors waiting out there.</i>

26:14.458 --> 26:17.041
<i>If you don't want that, then this…</i>

26:20.375 --> 26:21.541
<i>is wasted on you.</i>

26:25.166 --> 26:27.083
<i>[boy] "And if you don't want that,</i>

26:27.166 --> 26:29.000
<i>then this is wasted on ya."</i>

26:29.083 --> 26:31.666
<i>Ugh. That dorbel's full of shit.</i>

26:31.750 --> 26:34.000
<i>Master Deglan's preparing us for the Path.</i>

26:34.083 --> 26:36.208
<i>-Better hardship here than out there.</i>
<i>-[door opens]</i>

26:36.291 --> 26:37.541
<i>[grunts]</i>

26:37.625 --> 26:39.416
<i>Oh, there's a freeze tonight.</i>

26:39.500 --> 26:41.208
<i>-[horses snorting]</i>
<i>-[boy sobbing]</i>

26:42.333 --> 26:44.291
<i>Shut up and steal what sleep you can.</i>

26:46.291 --> 26:48.583
<i>Ah, don't mind Tomas.</i>

26:48.666 --> 26:49.958
<i>Law of Surprise.</i>

26:50.041 --> 26:52.875
<i>Didn't know he belonged to the witchers</i>
<i>till one came knocking.</i>

26:52.958 --> 26:54.125
<i>Law of Surprise?</i>

26:54.208 --> 26:57.750
<i>[boy] Fancy name for when you can't</i>
<i>pay a witcher. Give 'em your kid.</i>

26:59.166 --> 27:01.291
<i>[Vesemir] Were you sold,</i>
<i>or did you volunteer?</i>

27:01.375 --> 27:04.000
<i>[boy] Uh, my folks dumped me here.</i>
<i>Like most.</i>

27:04.083 --> 27:06.416
<i>Who chooses to be in this pigsty?</i>

27:09.833 --> 27:11.791
<i>-Don't be so scared.</i>
<i>-They're…</i>

27:12.500 --> 27:15.000
<i>-They're going to poison us.</i>
<i>-Who?</i>

27:15.083 --> 27:17.250
<i>[gasps] There are mages here.</i>

27:17.333 --> 27:18.250
<i>Old ones.</i>

27:18.833 --> 27:20.416
<i>Making witchers, they…</i>

27:20.500 --> 27:22.875
<i>They'll kill us. Then bring us back, but…</i>

27:23.458 --> 27:24.750
<i>we won't be normal.</i>

27:26.041 --> 27:29.000
<i>-They call it--</i>
<i>-The Trial of the Grasses. I know.</i>

27:29.083 --> 27:30.416
<i>I get scared too.</i>

27:31.291 --> 27:33.708
<i>Then I think,</i>
<i>"Soon, I'll be out on the Path,</i>

27:33.791 --> 27:36.666
<i>stronger than most anyone,</i>
<i>wanting for nothing."</i>

27:37.208 --> 27:38.541
<i>I'll never be scared again.</i>

27:39.208 --> 27:40.875
<i>[chuckles]</i>

27:40.958 --> 27:43.833
<i>You'll come out the Trials</i>
<i>better than normal, Tomas.</i>

27:44.708 --> 27:45.708
<i>On my word.</i>

27:57.083 --> 27:58.291
<i>[gasps]</i>

27:58.375 --> 27:59.625
<i>[coughing]</i>

28:04.125 --> 28:05.916
<i>-What the…</i>
<i>-[boy] It's Vesemir!</i>

28:08.791 --> 28:11.000
<i>[Vesemir groans] What's happened?</i>
<i>Where are we?</i>

28:11.083 --> 28:14.041
<i>Quiet.</i>
<i>My pa used to talk about this place.</i>

28:14.833 --> 28:16.333
<i>It's the Red Swamp.</i>

28:16.416 --> 28:17.625
<i>It's cursed.</i>

28:17.708 --> 28:20.666
<i>It's crawling</i>
<i>with evil spirits and beasts.</i>

28:21.250 --> 28:22.333
<i>Griffins.</i>

28:22.416 --> 28:23.875
<i>This is a test.</i>

28:24.500 --> 28:25.708
<i>Like all the others.</i>

28:25.791 --> 28:29.500
<i>On the Path,</i>
<i>a witcher's first instinct is to survive.</i>

28:30.083 --> 28:32.083
<i>It's about wits, not swords.</i>

28:32.166 --> 28:34.458
<i>We follow the moon until we're clear.</i>

28:34.541 --> 28:36.583
<i>If there's a monster close,</i>
<i>your medallion will--</i>

28:36.666 --> 28:38.125
<i>[ringing]</i>

28:48.583 --> 28:50.541
<i>-Wraiths!</i>
<i>-[Vesemir] Keep calm!</i>

28:51.708 --> 28:52.708
<i>Stay together!</i>

28:52.791 --> 28:54.166
<i>[screeching]</i>

28:55.208 --> 28:56.625
<i>[yelps]</i>

28:56.708 --> 28:58.458
<i>[wraiths screeching]</i>

29:11.166 --> 29:13.208
<i>-[ringing]</i>
<i>-Huh?</i>

29:19.625 --> 29:20.708
<i>[yells]</i>

29:21.541 --> 29:22.708
<i>[roars]</i>

29:22.791 --> 29:24.416
<i>-[yelps]</i>
<i>-[creature snarling]</i>

29:29.083 --> 29:30.333
<i>[boy groans]</i>

29:31.000 --> 29:31.833
<i>[sighs]</i>

29:34.750 --> 29:35.750
<i>This way.</i>

29:40.416 --> 29:42.541
<i>[creature snarling]</i>

29:47.625 --> 29:49.583
<i>[high-pitched ringing]</i>

29:50.250 --> 29:52.166
<i>[boys screaming]</i>

30:06.291 --> 30:07.125
<i>Uh…</i>

30:11.000 --> 30:12.500
<i>[Vesemir screaming]</i>

30:15.083 --> 30:16.166
<i>[gasps]</i>

30:16.833 --> 30:17.666
<i>[groans]</i>

30:19.000 --> 30:19.833
<i>Oh…</i>

30:20.958 --> 30:22.000
<i>[sighs]</i>

30:31.666 --> 30:32.500
<i>[gasps]</i>

30:34.083 --> 30:35.416
<i>[shudders]</i>

30:36.666 --> 30:38.666
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

30:53.500 --> 30:54.583
<i>[sobbing]</i>

30:57.208 --> 30:58.791
<i>[weeping]</i>

31:04.208 --> 31:05.958
<i>-[ringing]</i>
<i>-Oh!</i>

31:10.750 --> 31:12.750
<i>[medallion pulsing]</i>

31:22.125 --> 31:23.291
<i>[grunts]</i>

31:23.375 --> 31:25.000
<i>[low droning]</i>

31:41.125 --> 31:43.916
<i>The medallions sometimes sense</i>
<i>the bestiary.</i>

31:44.750 --> 31:47.666
<i>-Especially when it's full.</i>
<i>-[Vesemir] You're one of them.</i>

31:48.250 --> 31:50.625
<i>The mages Tomas mentioned</i>
<i>who make witchers.</i>

31:51.666 --> 31:53.041
<i>You don't look ancient.</i>

31:53.625 --> 31:55.708
<i>Well, mages age quite slowly.</i>

31:55.791 --> 31:56.916
<i>Witchers do too.</i>

31:57.000 --> 32:00.541
<i>Gives us both decades</i>
<i>to hone our respective skills.</i>

32:00.625 --> 32:01.916
<i>The Trials are only part</i>

32:02.000 --> 32:03.791
<i>-of my duty, though.</i>
<i>-[snarling]</i>

32:03.875 --> 32:05.500
<i>Don't fear.</i>

32:05.583 --> 32:08.916
<i>It's merely a side effect</i>
<i>of its hybrid genes.</i>

32:09.000 --> 32:10.750
<i>Krallachs. [chuckles]</i>

32:10.833 --> 32:14.208
<i>I've identified three different species</i>
<i>in this specimen's makeup.</i>

32:14.291 --> 32:16.625
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-It's a nasty little crossbreed.</i>

32:16.708 --> 32:20.458
<i>Master Deglan said</i>
<i>monsters can't mate with other species.</i>

32:20.958 --> 32:24.291
<i>True. Though they can be engineered.</i>

32:24.916 --> 32:27.708
<i>Imagine an army of beasts</i>

32:27.791 --> 32:30.916
<i>designed to wipe out</i>
<i>the elves and the Old Races</i>

32:31.000 --> 32:33.125
<i>to secure land and food.</i>

32:33.708 --> 32:35.208
<i>The alchemy was…</i>

32:35.291 --> 32:36.583
<i>inelegant, though.</i>

32:37.250 --> 32:39.708
<i>Most crossbreeds died instantly.</i>

32:40.666 --> 32:42.458
<i>[Vesemir] Mages made monsters,</i>

32:42.541 --> 32:44.666
<i>then made witchers to kill them?</i>

32:45.458 --> 32:48.458
<i>[mage] Today, my mages and I</i>
<i>guard the secrets</i>

32:48.541 --> 32:50.833
<i>to such mutagenic alchemy,</i>

32:50.916 --> 32:53.166
<i>preventing further abuse.</i>

32:53.833 --> 32:55.375
<i>I'm Reidrich, by the way.</i>

32:55.458 --> 32:57.208
<i>[Deglan] Are you daft, Reidrich?</i>

32:57.750 --> 33:01.541
<i>A witcher deserves</i>
<i>to understand its place in history.</i>

33:02.291 --> 33:04.500
<i>A rider came</i>
<i>while you were licking your wounds.</i>

33:04.583 --> 33:05.833
<i>Left a letter for ya.</i>

33:05.916 --> 33:09.125
<i>Did you know that Tomas and the others</i>
<i>would die in the swamp?</i>

33:09.208 --> 33:11.375
<i>It's a numbers game, young fella.</i>

33:11.458 --> 33:14.375
<i>-[faint growling]</i>
<i>-[Vesemir] How many survive these Trials?</i>

33:14.458 --> 33:17.041
<i>Depends. How many are witchers?</i>

33:18.750 --> 33:21.750
<i>Letter's by your cot.</i>
<i>Read it now, before I burn it.</i>

33:29.208 --> 33:30.458
<i>[Illyana] </i>"Vesemir."

33:31.083 --> 33:34.166
<i>"Your thoughts are likely far from here,</i>
<i>so I will be brief."</i>

33:35.083 --> 33:36.416
<i>"Your father is dead."</i>

33:37.125 --> 33:38.750
<i>"Kaedwen took our village </i>

33:38.833 --> 33:41.166
<i>and he was killed</i>
<i>while helping the lord and lady escape,</i>

33:41.250 --> 33:43.333
<i>-both of whom were also slain."</i>
-[child yelling]

33:43.833 --> 33:46.000
<i>-</i>[wailing]
<i>-"Do not return home, Vesemir,</i>

33:46.083 --> 33:48.416
<i>if this were ever that to you."</i>

33:49.458 --> 33:52.625
<i>"I hope you have found warmth</i>
<i>and comfort in this brittle world</i>

33:53.125 --> 33:56.958
<i>and that the world is being kind to you,</i>
<i>and most of all, fair."</i>

33:57.875 --> 34:02.041
<i>"For me, a noble family from Kaedwen</i>
<i>has claimed me theirs."</i>

34:03.125 --> 34:04.791
<i>"They are kinder masters."</i>

34:05.291 --> 34:09.000
<i>"They let me paint and show me how</i>
<i>to read words, as well as write a few."</i>

34:10.041 --> 34:12.000
<i>"I am well-fed and at peace."</i>

34:14.375 --> 34:16.875
<i>"There was little to miss</i>
<i>in our burnt-out town,</i>

34:16.958 --> 34:20.000
<i>and our snowball fights</i>
<i>and alleyway desserts</i>

34:20.083 --> 34:23.500
<i>are heavy memories</i>
<i>I now happily lay to rest."</i>

34:24.541 --> 34:26.541
<i>[echoing] </i>"Find your rebirth, Vesemir,

34:27.291 --> 34:29.375
<i>free of past burdens and hurts."</i>

34:30.208 --> 34:31.333
<i>"And yes,</i>

34:32.291 --> 34:33.500
<i>free of me."</i>

34:34.500 --> 34:35.833
<i>"It is best that way."</i>

34:37.333 --> 34:38.583
<i>"Live and love well."</i>

34:39.541 --> 34:40.458
<i>"Illyana."</i>

34:49.166 --> 34:51.083
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

34:59.625 --> 35:02.125
<i>-[howls]</i>
<i>-[dramatic music continues]</i>

35:17.500 --> 35:19.500
<i>[dramatic music continues]</i>

35:46.416 --> 35:48.541
<i>[indistinct screaming]</i>

35:53.791 --> 35:57.916
<i>Right. So, who wishes to ride</i>
<i>and get blitzed somewhere nice and quiet?</i>

35:58.000 --> 36:01.500
<i>[sighs] We stay and see who survives.</i>

36:01.583 --> 36:03.250
<i>[scoffs] That could take days.</i>

36:03.750 --> 36:05.250
<i>It'll be Eskel, Lambert,</i>

36:05.791 --> 36:06.833
<i>maybe Remus.</i>

36:07.416 --> 36:10.708
<i>Now, can we please go</i>
<i>get right properly drunk?</i>

36:10.791 --> 36:12.291
<i>[Luka] Oh, let them sulk.</i>

36:12.916 --> 36:13.916
<i>We'll drink.</i>

36:16.583 --> 36:18.083
<i>[Vesemir laughing]</i>

36:18.166 --> 36:21.458
<i>The midwife almost fainted</i>
<i>when I came for my payment.</i>

36:21.541 --> 36:24.958
<i>-[woman giggling]</i>
<i>-I looked an awful terror, red and sticky,</i>

36:25.041 --> 36:27.708
<i>but, you know, that's the job.</i>

36:27.791 --> 36:30.041
<i>[woman] And the striga? Was she cured?</i>

36:30.125 --> 36:31.666
<i>[Vesemir] Yes. Yes, of course.</i>

36:32.666 --> 36:35.041
<i>We need more before the next tale.</i>

36:36.625 --> 36:39.833
<i>You know, that midwife</i>
<i>should've hired a better savior.</i>

36:39.916 --> 36:41.458
<i>A man of virtue and honor.</i>

36:42.041 --> 36:43.125
<i>A real man.</i>

36:43.208 --> 36:44.833
<i>Not a mutant.</i>

36:44.916 --> 36:47.583
<i>Are knights being schooled</i>
<i>in striga curses now?</i>

36:48.208 --> 36:51.500
<i>Where'd that lesson fit?</i>
<i>Between learning curtsy and joust?</i>

36:51.583 --> 36:55.041
<i>We're all here for a little drink</i>
<i>and non-violent fun.</i>

36:56.833 --> 36:57.958
<i>Ugh.</i>

36:58.041 --> 37:00.916
<i>Is this the "your kind" bit?</i>

37:01.958 --> 37:03.583
<i>You frighten these people.</i>

37:04.083 --> 37:06.625
<i>As you frightened</i>
<i>that midwife you swindled.</i>

37:07.208 --> 37:08.666
<i>Best you leave.</i>

37:08.750 --> 37:11.083
<i>Right now.</i>

37:11.166 --> 37:13.541
<i>I've seen knights try to do our job.</i>

37:14.125 --> 37:15.833
<i>Tidy up monsters.</i>

37:15.916 --> 37:18.083
<i>Cautionary tales, all of you.</i>

37:18.166 --> 37:19.125
<i>[snorts]</i>

37:19.208 --> 37:20.708
<i>Especially the cute ones.</i>

37:20.791 --> 37:21.833
<i>[growls]</i>

37:23.833 --> 37:28.000
<i>The two witchers should be tried</i>
<i>and executed. No questions asked.</i>

37:28.083 --> 37:29.625
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Silly me.</i>

37:29.708 --> 37:33.791
<i>Here I thought</i>
<i>trials were all about questions.</i>

37:33.875 --> 37:37.333
<i>These two killed two of your guard,</i>
<i>Your Highness. You'd let that stand?</i>

37:37.416 --> 37:41.250
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Sire, the barkeep claims</i>
<i>your knights instigated the altercation.</i>

37:41.833 --> 37:44.583
<i>These witchers were defending themselves.</i>

37:45.291 --> 37:49.375
<i>The people's faith in the monarchy</i>
<i>already wavers due to the forest attacks.</i>

37:49.458 --> 37:53.083
<i>Now they'll hear the crown waxed idly</i>
<i>as two monsters shed knighted blood.</i>

37:53.166 --> 37:55.083
<i>So we should go to war with the witchers?</i>

37:55.166 --> 37:57.833
<i>If only so you can</i>
<i>make them what you fear?</i>

37:58.750 --> 38:01.250
<i>They are deadly. On that, we agree, Tetra.</i>

38:01.875 --> 38:04.750
<i>And such a battle would flood Kaedwen red.</i>

38:05.291 --> 38:08.375
<i>[Tetra] The Assembly should remember</i>
<i>the lady's seat here is honorary.</i>

38:08.458 --> 38:11.666
<i>-[attendants murmuring]</i>
<i>-Yet it is still my chair.</i>

38:11.750 --> 38:15.083
<i>Earned by her body. Not by blood or title.</i>

38:15.166 --> 38:17.625
<i>[groans] Gods, quiet!</i>

38:18.375 --> 38:21.500
<i>I'll have my knights kill you both</i>
<i>for the sake of my ears.</i>

38:21.583 --> 38:24.166
<i>Tetra's right, actually, sire.</i>

38:24.916 --> 38:27.375
<i>Your subjects expect action.</i>

38:27.458 --> 38:30.583
<i>What if you act</i>
<i>on two fronts with one move?</i>

38:30.666 --> 38:34.625
<i>Clear out our forests</i>
<i>while also avoiding war with the witchers?</i>

38:36.041 --> 38:38.000
<i>[stone clinks]</i>

38:38.875 --> 38:39.791
<i>[man groans]</i>

38:42.333 --> 38:43.958
<i>-Guard?</i>
<i>-[guard grunts]</i>

38:44.041 --> 38:45.250
<i>Aye?</i>

38:46.166 --> 38:47.333
<i>Do you hear that?</i>

38:47.416 --> 38:49.666
<i>-It's like this pinging noise.</i>
<i>-Hey!</i>

38:50.416 --> 38:53.333
<i>Are you eager for a beating, mutant?</i>

38:53.416 --> 38:56.875
<i>I'd settle for a pot to piss in</i>
<i>and some halfway decent bread, please.</i>

38:59.000 --> 38:59.833
<i>Oof!</i>

39:00.541 --> 39:01.375
<i>[door closes]</i>

39:01.958 --> 39:04.333
<i>Ah. A bit generous, but…</i>

39:11.250 --> 39:13.166
<i>[Lady Zerbst] No need to split this one.</i>

39:13.666 --> 39:15.375
<i>Not like when we were younger.</i>

39:15.458 --> 39:16.416
<i>[laughs]</i>

39:16.500 --> 39:21.041
<i>I knew witchers aged differently,</i>
<i>but, well, look at you!</i>

39:22.500 --> 39:23.541
<i>Illyana!</i>

39:23.625 --> 39:27.333
<i>No doubt you imagined me</i>
<i>an old spinster by now, slaving away.</i>

39:28.083 --> 39:30.333
<i>That is if you ever imagine me at all.</i>

39:30.416 --> 39:31.625
<i>Uh… your letter.</i>

39:32.750 --> 39:35.125
<i>-You'd been sold to a new estate.</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

39:35.791 --> 39:37.333
<i>The Zerbsts of Kaedwen.</i>

39:37.416 --> 39:39.333
<i>They were kind enough, but it…</i>

39:39.416 --> 39:43.000
<i>it was their son who was</i>
<i>truly fond of me, despite my station.</i>

39:44.333 --> 39:47.083
<i>[sighs] It's been an age.</i>
<i>Did you ever get that lake house?</i>

39:47.166 --> 39:50.583
<i>Lake house? Oh, my, the lake house!</i>

39:50.666 --> 39:52.375
<i>No lake, no.</i>

39:53.166 --> 39:54.250
<i>But a nice home.</i>

39:54.833 --> 39:57.750
<i>Turned it into an orphanage</i>
<i>after my husband passed.</i>

39:57.833 --> 40:00.208
<i>We had children too. Girls.</i>

40:00.291 --> 40:02.500
<i>Horrors, all three of them.</i>

40:02.583 --> 40:05.041
<i>One just made me a grandmother.</i>
<i>I begged her not to. </i>

40:05.125 --> 40:07.500
<i>[chuckles] But they're</i>
<i>stubborn little needlers.</i>

40:07.583 --> 40:09.458
<i>They often remind me of you--</i>

40:10.041 --> 40:11.375
<i>Oh, gods.</i>

40:11.875 --> 40:13.750
<i>I'm… rambling.</i>

40:14.250 --> 40:15.166
<i>You're bored.</i>

40:15.250 --> 40:16.958
<i>No, no, no. You're fine.</i>

40:17.041 --> 40:20.291
<i>You're good. Uh… this is unexpected, yes.</i>

40:20.791 --> 40:23.708
<i>Little fresh. But, uh… also lovely.</i>

40:24.208 --> 40:25.625
<i>You've had such a full--</i>

40:25.708 --> 40:30.208
<i>You wish to kill my already-dead husband</i>
<i>and burn the orphanage to the ground.</i>

40:31.166 --> 40:33.333
<i>Not the precise words I'd use.</i>

40:33.875 --> 40:35.125
<i>[laughs]</i>

40:36.583 --> 40:38.750
<i>Lord Zerbst was kind to me.</i>

40:39.708 --> 40:41.416
<i>By no means perfect, but…</i>

40:42.083 --> 40:46.125
<i>he's someone you miss very much</i>
<i>when they depart.</i>

40:48.416 --> 40:50.750
<i>The tales I've heard of you, though.</i>

40:51.250 --> 40:54.166
<i>The swashbuckling witcher for hire.</i>

40:54.250 --> 40:56.250
<i>"The slayer Vesemir,</i>

40:56.333 --> 40:59.333
<i>priced only for the foulest of creatures."</i>

40:59.416 --> 41:03.375
<i>Well, not too long ago, you were stuffing</i>
<i>my head full of those very notions.</i>

41:04.291 --> 41:06.750
<i>Years do work differently for you.</i>

41:06.833 --> 41:08.666
<i>[scoffs] What's time, anyway?</i>

41:09.833 --> 41:11.750
<i>-Everything.</i>
<i>-[door opens]</i>

41:12.750 --> 41:16.791
<i>The king is willing to grant you</i>
<i>and your friend amnesty for your crimes.</i>

41:16.875 --> 41:19.375
<i>Then you are reminded</i>
<i>that I carry the duties</i>

41:19.458 --> 41:23.666
<i>of my late husband, the noble Lord Zerbst,</i>
<i>adviser to the throne.</i>

41:23.750 --> 41:26.000
<i>Every deal has a price.</i>

41:26.083 --> 41:29.833
<i>Kill whatever is murdering our people</i>
<i>in the woods outside Ard Carraigh.</i>

41:29.916 --> 41:31.333
<i>And my colleague, Luka?</i>

41:31.416 --> 41:33.958
<i>-He'll have my care.</i>
<i>-Reasonable terms.</i>

41:34.541 --> 41:36.333
<i>You'll take a chaperone too.</i>

41:36.416 --> 41:38.125
<i>That, there, well…</i>

41:39.000 --> 41:40.000
<i>that's a problem.</i>

41:40.541 --> 41:42.250
<i>The Path's quite perilous,</i>

41:42.333 --> 41:45.500
<i>and you are a lady, my lady.</i>

41:46.333 --> 41:48.958
<i>Also, can't have a noble such as you</i>

41:49.041 --> 41:51.833
<i>seen slumming about</i>
<i>with the mutant likes of me.</i>

41:52.416 --> 41:56.000
<i>Then you'll no doubt be pleased</i>
<i>to hear that I am not your chaperone.</i>

42:02.166 --> 42:05.291
<i>I have no intention</i>
<i>of playing guide or nurse to you, witch.</i>

42:05.375 --> 42:07.416
<i>I don't care</i>
<i>who your great-great-whoever was.</i>

42:12.791 --> 42:13.708
<i>On my word,</i>

42:14.500 --> 42:16.083
<i>I will slay this beast.</i>

42:16.166 --> 42:17.416
<i>For you, Illyana.</i>

42:30.583 --> 42:32.416
<i>[Vesemir] Might not be a monster</i>
<i>at all, either.</i>

42:32.500 --> 42:35.625
<i>The leshen that killed your man Carlisle</i>
<i>was bewitched.</i>

42:35.708 --> 42:36.958
<i>By an elf.</i>

42:37.041 --> 42:39.500
<i>-[Tetra groans]</i>
<i>-"Why an elf?" Ah! Glad you asked.</i>

42:39.583 --> 42:42.375
<i>See, another very old</i>
<i>but very young-looking elf</i>

42:42.458 --> 42:46.041
<i>asked me to help him</i>
<i>to find a group of misplaced girls.</i>

42:47.208 --> 42:50.166
<i>Point is, witchering is a business.</i>

42:50.250 --> 42:51.583
<i>You have to keep a brand.</i>

42:51.666 --> 42:56.166
<i>Can't score the big jobs if you're known</i>
<i>for swatting nymphs and helping out elves.</i>

42:58.250 --> 43:00.708
<i>Isn't fire magic forbidden</i>
<i>by upstanding mages?</i>

43:01.750 --> 43:04.125
<i>Only insofar as</i>
<i>there are very few mages blessed</i>

43:04.208 --> 43:06.208
<i>with the skill to control the flames.</i>

43:08.000 --> 43:10.333
<i>[chewing] Huh.</i>
<i>You're very special, clearly.</i>

43:11.125 --> 43:12.541
<i>[burps and grunts]</i>

43:13.125 --> 43:14.625
<i>I must seem silly to you.</i>

43:15.416 --> 43:16.791
<i>But Chaos, it's…</i>

43:17.708 --> 43:20.208
<i>Well, words fail description.</i>

43:21.833 --> 43:24.125
<i>Witchers are connected to Chaos too.</i>

43:24.208 --> 43:27.208
<i>Only your connection</i>
<i>is corrupted and corrosive.</i>

43:27.291 --> 43:28.416
<i>And far less condemning.</i>

43:32.291 --> 43:36.166
<i>There's a story about a witcher</i>
<i>who helped an ailing priest.</i>

43:36.708 --> 43:40.000
<i>The monster-slayer believed</i>
<i>the sickness was, in fact, a curse,</i>

43:41.416 --> 43:43.833
<i>and could be lifted</i>
<i>by killing whoever placed it.</i>

43:44.333 --> 43:47.041
<i>The priest quickly fingered</i>
<i>a local sorceress,</i>

43:47.125 --> 43:49.375
<i>a stupid girl</i>
<i>who always caused him trouble.</i>

43:50.291 --> 43:54.166
<i>The witcher killed her,</i>
<i>and was rightly paid in gems and jewels.</i>

43:55.958 --> 43:58.833
<i>-The priest obviously got better.</i>
<i>-He did.</i>

43:59.416 --> 44:01.166
<i>And then a few days later,</i>

44:01.250 --> 44:04.958
<i>he found a beautiful gem</i>
<i>amid his cook's belongings,</i>

44:05.041 --> 44:08.166
<i>identical to the one</i>
<i>he'd given the clever witcher.</i>

44:08.250 --> 44:10.666
<i>Ah. He had the cook poison</i>
<i>the priest's meals.</i>

44:10.750 --> 44:12.333
<i>Cut him in on the take.</i>

44:12.416 --> 44:15.166
<i>[exclaims] Smart con.</i>
<i>Wish I'd thought of it.</i>

44:15.875 --> 44:16.916
<i>As I said…</i>

44:17.666 --> 44:18.541
<i>corrupted.</i>

44:30.000 --> 44:30.875
<i>Ah, lovely.</i>

44:31.500 --> 44:33.166
<i>-You've led us in a circle.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

44:33.750 --> 44:35.416
<i>I know these forests.</i>

44:35.500 --> 44:37.458
<i>Hmm. So did Lord Carlisle.</i>

44:37.541 --> 44:41.958
<i>At Aretuza, we used magic to cast pleasant</i>
<i>illusions around unpleasant foods.</i>

44:42.041 --> 44:43.791
<i>Made food tastier,</i>

44:43.875 --> 44:46.041
<i>yet the aftertaste of the illusion?</i>

44:48.208 --> 44:49.041
<i>Bitter.</i>

44:51.333 --> 44:56.458
<i>Chaos clear our hearts and minds.</i>
<i>Let our eyes see right and true.</i>

44:57.125 --> 44:59.166
<i>Lift the shroud that cloaks our mind.</i>

44:59.250 --> 45:00.083
<i>[horse neighing]</i>

45:00.166 --> 45:02.750
<i>-Lift the shroud that cloaks our mind!</i>
<i>-[booming]</i>

45:16.125 --> 45:18.458
<i>That illusion was flawless.</i>

45:19.166 --> 45:21.791
<i>The power needed to maintain such art…</i>

45:22.458 --> 45:24.458
<i>[Vesemir] Could also bewitch a leshen.</i>

45:26.250 --> 45:28.250
<i>[ringing]</i>

45:34.083 --> 45:37.500
<i>Garean bhaedh aip me vhoelynath.</i>

45:37.583 --> 45:39.625
<i>-Kitsu?</i>
<i>-Friend of yours?</i>

45:39.708 --> 45:40.958
<i>Friend of a friend.</i>

45:41.041 --> 45:44.000
<i>Garean bhaedh aip me vhoelynath!</i>

45:44.083 --> 45:48.375
<i>Yes. I'll need to know what</i>
<i>and where your den is if I'm to avoid it,</i>

45:48.458 --> 45:50.375
<i>especially since you're, you know,</i>

45:50.458 --> 45:52.166
<i>-slaughtering people over it.</i>
<i>-Witcher.</i>

45:54.791 --> 45:56.625
<i>[roars]</i>

45:56.708 --> 45:58.916
<i>I've never seen</i>
<i>such a species of basilisk.</i>

45:59.416 --> 46:01.875
<i>-Another illusion?</i>
<i>-We'll no doubt find out shortly.</i>

46:02.833 --> 46:04.833
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

46:06.083 --> 46:08.083
<i>[screeching]</i>

46:13.666 --> 46:15.166
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-[screeches]</i>

46:17.250 --> 46:18.083
<i>[beast grunts]</i>

46:30.250 --> 46:31.750
<i>[roaring]</i>

46:34.958 --> 46:37.750
<i>I know. She has that effect on everyone.</i>

46:37.833 --> 46:39.541
<i>But still, manners.</i>

46:49.791 --> 46:50.625
<i>[groans]</i>

47:06.416 --> 47:07.708
<i>[screeches]</i>

47:09.750 --> 47:10.916
<i>[creature trilling]</i>

47:13.500 --> 47:14.750
<i>[coughs]</i>

47:17.375 --> 47:18.291
<i>[growling]</i>

47:21.958 --> 47:24.041
<i>[dramatic music continues]</i>

47:30.333 --> 47:31.416
<i>[Vesemir grunts]</i>

47:33.083 --> 47:34.333
<i>[screeching]</i>

47:34.416 --> 47:35.875
<i>[hissing]</i>

47:46.333 --> 47:47.291
<i>[sighs]</i>

47:50.750 --> 47:52.000
<i>[Kitsu] No!</i>

47:52.083 --> 47:54.416
<i>No! [sobs]</i>

47:55.083 --> 47:57.791
<i>-It was real.</i>
<i>-Might have slightly underestimated you.</i>

47:58.291 --> 47:59.416
<i>Slightly.</i>

48:00.416 --> 48:01.916
<i>-Ah.</i>
<i>-[Kitsu crying]</i>

48:02.500 --> 48:04.708
<i>Kitsu, this needn't escalate.</i>

48:04.791 --> 48:06.125
<i>[Kitsu sobbing]</i>

48:10.083 --> 48:11.708
<i>[rumbling]</i>

48:11.791 --> 48:12.958
<i>Uh…</i>

48:15.291 --> 48:16.458
<i>[exclaims]</i>

48:18.958 --> 48:19.916
<i>Oh!</i>

48:27.333 --> 48:28.583
<i>[gasps]</i>

48:34.375 --> 48:35.541
<i>Witcher!</i>

48:39.166 --> 48:40.166
<i>[knife whistling]</i>

48:50.291 --> 48:51.416
<i>[sighs]</i>

48:59.583 --> 49:02.291
<i>Her powers of illusion are unnatural.</i>

49:02.375 --> 49:04.750
<i>First monster</i>
<i>I ever encountered was a mahr.</i>

49:04.833 --> 49:08.458
<i>Made a woman see nightmares</i>
<i>that weren't really there. Illusions.</i>

49:08.541 --> 49:11.875
<i>-Kitsu's an elf.</i>
<i>-Then why does she smell like a mahr?</i>

49:13.333 --> 49:15.333
<i>[Vesemir and Tetra panting]</i>

49:19.708 --> 49:20.916
<i>[Tetra] An elven school.</i>

49:21.625 --> 49:24.291
<i>They used to send their young here</i>
<i>during high summer.</i>

49:24.958 --> 49:29.041
<i>Before repurposing it as a garrison</i>
<i>during your last cleansing spree.</i>

49:31.666 --> 49:32.916
<i>No signs of blood.</i>

49:34.625 --> 49:36.375
<i>I can still smell her, though.</i>

49:37.041 --> 49:37.875
<i>Yes.</i>

49:38.375 --> 49:39.375
<i>She was here.</i>

49:40.250 --> 49:41.583
<i>Just before our fight.</i>

50:19.541 --> 50:20.416
<i>Witcher!</i>

50:21.166 --> 50:22.666
<i>I do have a name, you know.</i>

50:22.750 --> 50:24.500
<i>[gasps] Ugh!</i>

50:28.416 --> 50:29.875
<i>What was done to them?</i>

50:31.833 --> 50:33.250
<i>[Vesemir] They're all elves.</i>

50:34.000 --> 50:35.000
<i>Girls.</i>

50:35.083 --> 50:36.500
<i>[man] Over here.</i>

50:36.583 --> 50:37.416
<i>Help.</i>

50:48.458 --> 50:50.500
<i>Gods, not another favor.</i>

50:52.333 --> 50:53.250
<i>Who's this one?</i>

50:54.458 --> 50:57.875
<i>[Vesemir] My aforementioned friend.</i>
<i>He was searching for those girls.</i>

50:58.875 --> 51:03.041
<i>And I could've saved some, had you</i>
<i>set aside your love of coin and helped.</i>

51:03.541 --> 51:08.083
<i>-[Vesemir] Kitsu's been kidnapping them.</i>
<i>-Yes. Experimenting on the girls.</i>

51:08.166 --> 51:10.916
<i>She's using some strange alchemy</i>
<i>to try to change them.</i>

51:11.916 --> 51:13.750
<i>Change them to what?</i>

51:13.833 --> 51:15.458
<i>Into whatever she's become.</i>

51:16.333 --> 51:20.083
<i>I tracked her here,</i>
<i>tried stopping her, but… Kitsu's power…</i>

51:20.166 --> 51:21.750
<i>And she just let you live?</i>

51:21.833 --> 51:25.541
<i>I understand if that's a concept</i>
<i>unfamiliar to your kind.</i>

51:25.625 --> 51:28.541
<i>If Kitsu was using sorcery</i>
<i>to try and mutate those girls,</i>

51:28.625 --> 51:29.791
<i>who mutated her?</i>

51:33.541 --> 51:36.458
<i>Her genes were spliced</i>
<i>with those of a mahr.</i>

51:37.125 --> 51:39.041
<i>It explains her unnatural power.</i>

51:39.666 --> 51:40.916
<i>She's a crossbreed.</i>

51:41.000 --> 51:42.708
<i>How is such a thing possible?</i>

51:42.791 --> 51:44.375
<i>The same way he was made.</i>

51:45.166 --> 51:46.583
<i>Mutagenic alchemy.</i>

51:46.666 --> 51:49.500
<i>Its secrets known</i>
<i>only to mages at Kaer Morhen.</i>

51:49.583 --> 51:51.208
<i>You're behind all this.</i>

51:51.291 --> 51:52.375
<i>That's ridiculous.</i>

51:53.833 --> 51:56.875
<i>-[grunts]</i>
<i>-Hunting monsters for coin wasn't enough?</i>

51:57.541 --> 51:59.041
<i>Now you make them?</i>

51:59.125 --> 52:00.875
<i>Witchers are struggling, yes, but…</i>

52:02.083 --> 52:06.458
<i>Shame. A few new beasts would be…</i>
<i>good for business.</i>

52:07.666 --> 52:10.250
<i>[Tetra] More monsters,</i>
<i>more jobs, more coin.</i>

52:10.333 --> 52:11.708
<i>Another sharp con.</i>

52:11.791 --> 52:13.708
<i>-I swear, Fil, I didn't--</i>
<i>-[rustling]</i>

52:21.291 --> 52:22.666
<i>Another monstrosity.</i>

52:24.875 --> 52:26.041
<i>[grunts]</i>

52:26.125 --> 52:27.125
<i>[shudders]</i>

52:27.625 --> 52:28.791
<i>She's still an elf.</i>

52:30.333 --> 52:31.208
<i>[sighs]</i>

52:33.375 --> 52:35.166
<i>You saw what these creatures can do.</i>

52:35.750 --> 52:38.375
<i>Fil, if the girl has</i>
<i>even half Kitsu's power,</i>

52:38.958 --> 52:40.250
<i>she's dangerous.</i>

52:40.333 --> 52:42.625
<i>Doesn't this witch say similar of you?</i>

52:43.750 --> 52:47.416
<i>I will take her back to my people.</i>
<i>She will be raised as an elf.</i>

52:47.500 --> 52:48.333
<i>[Tetra] Charitable.</i>

52:48.416 --> 52:52.083
<i>Though I imagine it won't be too long</i>
<i>before you sic her on us.</i>

52:52.166 --> 52:53.375
<i>[Filavandrel] You won.</i>

52:54.583 --> 52:56.083
<i>You beat us.</i>

52:56.166 --> 52:57.833
<i>At least allow us the indignity</i>

52:57.916 --> 53:01.250
<i>of scavenging whatever's left of our kind,</i>
<i>mutant or otherwise.</i>

53:02.541 --> 53:04.541
<i>As a favor to a friend.</i>

53:07.041 --> 53:09.166
<i>Take the child and go. Now.</i>

53:10.708 --> 53:13.083
<i>You have made a serious error.</i>

53:13.875 --> 53:16.291
<i>Should that girl ever harm</i>
<i>a single soul, Fil--</i>

53:16.375 --> 53:17.750
<i>Then I will slay her.</i>

53:18.375 --> 53:21.333
<i>Quietly welcome you and your sword.</i>

53:24.208 --> 53:27.416
<i>I should've offered up some coin.</i>
<i>Then you would've handled matters.</i>

53:27.500 --> 53:29.375
<i>It was not a question of price.</i>

53:30.666 --> 53:32.875
<i>Oh, the witcher's found his morals?</i>

53:32.958 --> 53:36.000
<i>You think you're so pure, Tetra?</i>
<i>Not a blemish?</i>

53:36.083 --> 53:38.625
<i>Look outside. There's your morality.</i>

53:39.291 --> 53:41.625
<i>Rot and ruin all reeking of hate.</i>

53:42.125 --> 53:44.250
<i>Tend to that filth, and I'll tend to mine.</i>

54:05.583 --> 54:07.583
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

54:41.125 --> 54:43.125
<i>[dramatic music continues]</i>

54:48.666 --> 54:50.833
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Nothing good</i>
<i>can come of this.</i>

54:51.458 --> 54:53.375
<i>[Vesemir] Fear and ignorance</i>
<i>are good business.</i>

54:53.458 --> 54:55.625
<i>That's what Deglan said</i>
<i>the first time we met.</i>

54:56.166 --> 54:57.041
<i>Now look.</i>

54:58.041 --> 54:59.458
<i>I need to know for certain.</i>

55:00.666 --> 55:03.041
<i>[Lady Zerbst] I'd ask you to flee with me.</i>

55:07.166 --> 55:08.791
<i>I know what you have to do.</i>

55:09.458 --> 55:13.750
<i>And I won't have you feeling</i>
<i>as though you've abandoned me again.</i>

55:18.000 --> 55:20.000
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

55:39.833 --> 55:42.458
<i>-[growling]</i>
<i>-[Tetra] I tried to stop him.</i>

55:42.541 --> 55:45.750
<i>-[hisses]</i>
<i>-But witchers, they never hesitate.</i>

55:49.833 --> 55:52.375
<i>[king] Madam Gilcrest has given proof.</i>

55:52.458 --> 55:54.625
<i>This one breeds monstrosities,</i>

55:54.708 --> 55:56.500
<i>terrorizes my kingdom,</i>

55:57.083 --> 55:59.375
<i>and swindles the people.</i>

55:59.916 --> 56:01.208
<i>[grunting]</i>

56:01.708 --> 56:03.833
<i>What the hell are you talking about?</i>

56:04.416 --> 56:07.791
<i>Sire, not all witchers were aware</i>
<i>of these crossbreeds.</i>

56:07.875 --> 56:10.833
<i>Lady Zerbst,</i>
<i>you are testament to the perils</i>

56:10.916 --> 56:13.958
<i>of trusting a servant.</i>

56:15.208 --> 56:16.166
<i>Your Highness--</i>

56:19.416 --> 56:21.458
<i>If it pleases, sire,</i>

56:21.541 --> 56:24.916
<i>might I ask where Madam Gilcrest is now?</i>

56:52.125 --> 56:54.125
<i>[liquid bubbling]</i>

57:11.375 --> 57:12.958
<i>[creature trilling]</i>

57:22.083 --> 57:24.333
<i>[Deglan] Monsters were going extinct.</i>

57:24.416 --> 57:26.083
<i>I had to protect our way of life.</i>

57:27.208 --> 57:29.666
<i>Think of all the coin</i>
<i>you stand to make, young fella.</i>

57:29.750 --> 57:32.791
<i>-Do not call me that.</i>
<i>-Check your gratitude, boy.</i>

57:32.875 --> 57:34.000
<i>You came to me.</i>

57:34.083 --> 57:36.916
<i>I could've shipped you right back</i>
<i>to those bedpans.</i>

57:37.000 --> 57:39.333
<i>Don't pretend you didn't know</i>
<i>exactly what you were doing</i>

57:39.416 --> 57:40.916
<i>when you threw me those coins.</i>

57:41.000 --> 57:42.291
<i>You knew I would come.</i>

57:43.000 --> 57:45.041
<i>We were created</i>
<i>to kill creatures like these,</i>

57:45.125 --> 57:46.375
<i>not to make them.</i>

57:46.458 --> 57:48.708
<i>I won't weep for doing what needed doing.</i>

57:49.333 --> 57:50.875
<i>I told you.</i>

57:50.958 --> 57:52.791
<i>[Vesemir] A witcher never hesitates.</i>

57:52.875 --> 57:53.958
<i>Oh, I know.</i>

57:54.041 --> 57:57.958
<i>What about with the elf? Did you give</i>
<i>Kitsu a choice before you mutated her?</i>

57:58.625 --> 58:00.333
<i>No, I thought we'd killed her.</i>

58:00.416 --> 58:03.375
<i>That mutation was unstable.</i>
<i>Too much power.</i>

58:04.041 --> 58:07.500
<i>Clearly, her death was one</i>
<i>of her clever little illusions.</i>

58:07.583 --> 58:09.500
<i>[Vesemir] All of this to line our pockets.</i>

58:09.583 --> 58:11.041
<i>[Deglan laughs]</i>

58:11.125 --> 58:14.041
<i>You were always too focused</i>
<i>on the gold in your hand.</i>

58:14.708 --> 58:17.833
<i>You never looked up</i>
<i>to see who's paying you. See their eyes.</i>

58:18.416 --> 58:19.333
<i>We terrify 'em.</i>

58:19.916 --> 58:23.000
<i>The only thing keeping men from hunting us</i>

58:23.583 --> 58:25.666
<i>are the scarier beasts we keep away.</i>

58:26.333 --> 58:31.416
<i>Humans die quick, so they spend</i>
<i>their lives fearing and hating.</i>

58:31.500 --> 58:33.916
<i>Ask the dwarves or your elf friend.</i>

58:34.000 --> 58:36.375
<i>Men will always need monsters.</i>

58:37.083 --> 58:39.625
<i>-Now, so do we.</i>
<i>-We're all orphans.</i>

58:39.708 --> 58:42.166
<i>We've always looked to you to protect us.</i>

58:42.250 --> 58:45.791
<i>You have to burn it to the ground…</i>
<i>or I will.</i>

58:45.875 --> 58:46.916
<i>[Deglan yelling]</i>

58:52.833 --> 58:54.333
<i>I don't want to fight you.</i>

58:54.416 --> 58:56.375
<i>We've got to protect ourselves, Vesemir.</i>

59:00.541 --> 59:01.791
<i>Got to protect you!</i>

59:08.666 --> 59:13.041
<i>If you two would like to stop</i>
<i>trying to kill each other,</i>

59:13.750 --> 59:15.208
<i>we have a visitor.</i>

59:17.750 --> 59:19.166
<i>[Lady Zerbst] She's coming.</i>

59:20.416 --> 59:22.416
<i>[hooves drumming]</i>

59:24.041 --> 59:25.708
<i>[mob yelling]</i>

59:28.333 --> 59:31.250
<i>-[mob clamoring]</i>
<i>-[man] Away with all witchers!</i>

59:31.833 --> 59:34.625
<i>Tetra wasted no time. Word spread quickly.</i>

59:35.291 --> 59:38.583
<i>Not only of the crossbreeds,</i>
<i>but of witchers protecting elves.</i>

59:39.083 --> 59:40.125
<i>And Luka?</i>

59:42.125 --> 59:43.500
<i>This is your two's doing.</i>

59:43.583 --> 59:46.250
<i>They were always gonna come,</i>
<i>sooner or later.</i>

59:46.333 --> 59:49.791
<i>[Vesemir] Well, maybe there was a way</i>
<i>for us to die the better men.</i>

59:49.875 --> 59:54.333
<i>My mages and I are the ones</i>
<i>who know the secrets to mutagenic alchemy.</i>

59:54.416 --> 59:56.916
<i>Tetra will want our heads most.</i>

59:57.000 --> 59:58.583
<i>If we die,</i>

59:59.208 --> 1:00:02.291
<i>there can be no more witchers.</i>

1:00:03.333 --> 1:00:05.291
<i>Seal yourselves in your labs.</i>

1:00:05.375 --> 1:00:07.875
<i>The rest of us will rally</i>
<i>and end her little cult.</i>

1:00:08.458 --> 1:00:09.708
<i>Bitch won't see dawn.</i>

1:00:11.750 --> 1:00:15.625
<i>Underestimate Tetra and you'll be the one</i>
<i>who's seen their last sunrise.</i>

1:00:20.458 --> 1:00:22.583
<i>[Vesemir] Perhaps she'll listen to reason.</i>

1:00:22.666 --> 1:00:26.291
<i>He may be a bastard… but Deglan is right.</i>

1:00:27.166 --> 1:00:28.458
<i>This was inevitable.</i>

1:00:28.541 --> 1:00:29.583
<i>Why?</i>

1:00:29.666 --> 1:00:31.666
<i>-Because you're different.</i>
<i>-[mob yelling]</i>

1:00:31.750 --> 1:00:34.125
<i>[Lady Zerbst] And killing</i>
<i>is easier than tolerating.</i>

1:00:36.416 --> 1:00:38.500
<i>I want you as far away from this place</i>
<i>as possible.</i>

1:00:38.583 --> 1:00:40.166
<i>There are children here.</i>

1:00:40.250 --> 1:00:43.416
<i>-They've been trained.</i>
<i>-Children, Vesemir.</i>

1:00:43.500 --> 1:00:45.416
<i>As you were when he took you.</i>

1:00:45.500 --> 1:00:48.583
<i>I'll guide them to the cellar</i>
<i>until the battle's won.</i>

1:00:49.166 --> 1:00:52.875
<i>For once, I will decide my place.</i>

1:00:53.708 --> 1:00:55.333
<i>You've always had too much fire.</i>

1:00:56.000 --> 1:00:57.166
<i>And beauty.</i>

1:00:57.250 --> 1:01:00.333
<i>Please… I'm nearly 70.</i>

1:01:05.041 --> 1:01:06.041
<i>So am I.</i>

1:01:09.416 --> 1:01:11.416
<i>[tranquil music playing]</i>

1:01:13.208 --> 1:01:15.208
<i>[wind whistling]</i>

1:01:19.291 --> 1:01:20.125
<i>[horse snorts]</i>

1:01:25.250 --> 1:01:27.250
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:01:31.833 --> 1:01:34.916
<i>Beautiful peaks. Too pure for war.</i>

1:01:35.000 --> 1:01:39.958
<i>Scurry off and return with the body</i>
<i>of the man you murdered, witch.</i>

1:01:40.041 --> 1:01:44.000
<i>He was executed in the name</i>
<i>of those your homemade beasts butchered.</i>

1:01:44.500 --> 1:01:46.666
<i>There'll be no more of them, Tetra.</i>

1:01:46.750 --> 1:01:47.666
<i>Upon my word.</i>

1:01:49.125 --> 1:01:51.541
<i>Well, witchers are experts in price.</i>

1:01:51.625 --> 1:01:54.166
<i>What is the worth of your word, Vesemir?</i>

1:01:54.250 --> 1:01:55.166
<i>Some things…</i>

1:01:56.083 --> 1:01:57.291
<i>are beyond cost.</i>

1:01:59.333 --> 1:02:00.166
<i>And you?</i>

1:02:01.083 --> 1:02:02.583
<i>Do you give me your word?</i>

1:02:03.125 --> 1:02:04.625
<i>I give you nothing.</i>

1:02:04.708 --> 1:02:09.500
<i>Save the chance to fill the valleys</i>
<i>of our pretty peaks with your corpses.</i>

1:02:10.291 --> 1:02:12.250
<i>We are an army of witchers.</i>

1:02:12.333 --> 1:02:13.541
<i>You are human.</i>

1:02:19.208 --> 1:02:21.041
<i>[wind sighing]</i>

1:02:25.000 --> 1:02:27.416
<i>[ominous music playing]</i>

1:02:32.416 --> 1:02:33.333
<i>[ringing]</i>

1:02:42.833 --> 1:02:44.166
<i>[snarling]</i>

1:02:44.250 --> 1:02:46.250
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:03:02.250 --> 1:03:03.208
<i>[Vesemir] Kitsu.</i>

1:03:03.291 --> 1:03:05.958
<i>[Tetra] She was gutted</i>
<i>to hear how you sacked her den,</i>

1:03:06.041 --> 1:03:09.791
<i>destroyed her work,</i>
<i>and murdered the girl, her only child.</i>

1:03:11.125 --> 1:03:12.791
<i>Monsters to fight monsters.</i>

1:03:13.416 --> 1:03:14.875
<i>How unlike your predecessors.</i>

1:03:24.916 --> 1:03:27.083
<i>[Deglan] Rally! Rally!</i>

1:03:27.166 --> 1:03:29.666
<i>Steel your nerves, lads. We charge!</i>

1:03:29.750 --> 1:03:32.875
<i>-[Vesemir] Swords away. Swords away!</i>
<i>-We haven't time to hesitate.</i>

1:03:32.958 --> 1:03:34.500
<i>Just bloody trust me for once!</i>

1:03:37.833 --> 1:03:38.791
<i>Please!</i>

1:03:43.166 --> 1:03:44.958
<i>Witchers, on me!</i>

1:03:46.875 --> 1:03:48.875
<i>[monsters growling and chittering]</i>

1:03:54.125 --> 1:03:56.041
<i>-Now!</i>
<i>-[low booming]</i>

1:04:04.166 --> 1:04:06.958
<i>-[Lady Zerbst] Be calm. Be calm.</i>
<i>-[low rumbling]</i>

1:04:07.041 --> 1:04:08.041
<i>You're safe.</i>

1:04:14.375 --> 1:04:16.375
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:04:38.583 --> 1:04:39.791
<i>[hissing]</i>

1:04:41.625 --> 1:04:42.458
<i>[yells]</i>

1:04:59.666 --> 1:05:02.500
<i>[monsters growling and chittering]</i>

1:05:05.750 --> 1:05:08.583
<i>Witchers must be wiped</i>
<i>from the surface of this Earth,</i>

1:05:08.666 --> 1:05:11.833
<i>and all traces strewn</i>
<i>with salt and saltpeter.</i>

1:05:38.125 --> 1:05:39.500
<i>[Deglan] She's going for Reidrich!</i>

1:05:40.583 --> 1:05:44.458
<i>Me and the others will hold the bridge.</i>
<i>Use the drop to halve their numbers.</i>

1:05:46.000 --> 1:05:48.083
<i>You two, stop her!</i>

1:05:49.291 --> 1:05:51.458
<i>Can you forgive me long enough,</i>
<i>young fella?</i>

1:05:51.541 --> 1:05:52.416
<i>[sighs angrily]</i>

1:06:08.708 --> 1:06:09.958
<i>[roaring]</i>

1:06:20.625 --> 1:06:23.375
<i>-[men screaming]</i>
<i>-[monsters chittering]</i>

1:06:23.458 --> 1:06:26.250
<i>[melancholy music playing]</i>

1:06:30.750 --> 1:06:32.750
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:06:33.958 --> 1:06:35.958
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:06:43.750 --> 1:06:44.750
<i>[grunts]</i>

1:06:51.458 --> 1:06:52.291
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:06:53.541 --> 1:06:55.666
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:07:13.541 --> 1:07:14.833
<i>[yells]</i>

1:07:35.916 --> 1:07:37.083
<i>[yells]</i>

1:07:53.833 --> 1:07:56.458
<i>[dramatic music continues]</i>

1:08:03.625 --> 1:08:06.041
<i>If she gets Reidrich, it's the end of us.</i>

1:08:08.625 --> 1:08:09.875
<i>Find her!</i>

1:08:11.583 --> 1:08:13.833
<i>-Stop her!</i>
<i>-[screaming]</i>

1:08:22.041 --> 1:08:23.625
<i>[rumbling]</i>

1:08:24.875 --> 1:08:26.875
<i>There's a hatch in the grain hold.</i>

1:08:26.958 --> 1:08:29.041
<i>It lets out on the back pathway.</i>

1:08:29.125 --> 1:08:30.375
<i>How do you know this?</i>

1:08:30.458 --> 1:08:32.000
<i>He was trying to run away!</i>

1:08:34.750 --> 1:08:36.666
<i>Run as far away as possible.</i>

1:08:36.750 --> 1:08:37.583
<i>All of you.</i>

1:08:37.666 --> 1:08:40.458
<i>Rub the heel raw,</i>
<i>to the bone, if you have to.</i>

1:08:40.541 --> 1:08:41.583
<i>Don't stop.</i>

1:08:50.833 --> 1:08:52.833
<i>[Reidrich praying in Elven Tongue]</i>

1:08:55.625 --> 1:08:57.291
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Lower your swords.</i>

1:08:59.541 --> 1:09:01.333
<i>This is genocide, Tetra.</i>

1:09:01.916 --> 1:09:06.125
<i>They bred those monsters because of you.</i>
<i>There is no purity here.</i>

1:09:06.208 --> 1:09:08.000
<i>Just fear and hatred.</i>

1:09:08.083 --> 1:09:10.541
<i>Enough, please!</i>

1:09:11.375 --> 1:09:14.041
<i>This servant betrays Kaedwen</i>
<i>to the witchers.</i>

1:09:15.000 --> 1:09:16.166
<i>Let her join them.</i>

1:09:23.000 --> 1:09:25.000
<i>[Vesemir yelling] Tetra!</i>

1:09:25.083 --> 1:09:27.458
<i>I can drop your men</i>
<i>before their blades drop an inch.</i>

1:09:27.541 --> 1:09:29.791
<i>[scoffs] Wishful thinking.</i>

1:09:32.916 --> 1:09:33.916
<i>[whooshing]</i>

1:09:39.541 --> 1:09:42.916
<i>Are you going to enjoy the day,</i>
<i>or are you still too shook</i>

1:09:43.000 --> 1:09:45.208
<i>from another daring night</i>
<i>of monster-slaying?</i>

1:09:45.708 --> 1:09:49.666
<i>[chuckles] Pardon me for wanting to be</i>
<i>something other than a churlish knave.</i>

1:09:50.166 --> 1:09:51.416
<i>Look at you, though.</i>

1:09:52.708 --> 1:09:54.041
<i>You're a witcher.</i>

1:09:54.791 --> 1:09:56.041
<i>You're rich!</i>

1:09:56.125 --> 1:09:57.208
<i>[coins clinking]</i>

1:09:57.291 --> 1:09:59.000
<i>We'll lack for nothing,</i>

1:09:59.541 --> 1:10:02.000
<i>and you'll take care of me, Vesemir.</i>

1:10:02.083 --> 1:10:04.875
<i>Much like you said. True to your word.</i>

1:10:08.875 --> 1:10:11.083
<i>-Look at me.</i>
<i>-A lake house.</i>

1:10:11.875 --> 1:10:14.208
<i>Wine. Food.</i>

1:10:14.291 --> 1:10:18.083
<i>Imagine the seas of coin we'd wade in.</i>

1:10:19.625 --> 1:10:22.416
<i>You never wanted that!</i>
<i>You were always content.</i>

1:10:23.000 --> 1:10:23.916
<i>No, no, no!</i>

1:10:26.125 --> 1:10:28.416
<i>[man] Forty tons of sheep's blood?</i>

1:10:29.166 --> 1:10:30.833
<i>That poor midwife!</i>

1:10:30.916 --> 1:10:34.875
<i>Oh, oh, tell 'em about the time</i>
<i>you swindled the Redanian priest.</i>

1:10:34.958 --> 1:10:37.208
<i>Had him thinking he was cursed!</i>

1:10:37.791 --> 1:10:41.875
<i>-How much did you take that fool for?</i>
<i>-You can't be here. We lost you.</i>

1:10:45.125 --> 1:10:46.833
<i>What are you prattling about?</i>

1:10:48.041 --> 1:10:52.750
<i>[cackles] Wake the barkeep,</i>
<i>drain the barrels. Everyone drink!</i>

1:10:53.583 --> 1:10:55.583
<i>Not a coin spared.</i>

1:10:55.666 --> 1:10:58.000
<i>-[man] Yeah!</i>
<i>-[men cackling and cheering]</i>

1:11:02.291 --> 1:11:04.458
<i>Enough! All of you!</i>

1:11:04.541 --> 1:11:06.166
<i>Stop… stop cackling!</i>

1:11:06.250 --> 1:11:08.000
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Vesemir, come look.</i>

1:11:10.125 --> 1:11:11.166
<i>Be honest, now.</i>

1:11:11.250 --> 1:11:14.333
<i>Well, don't just stand there. Say it.</i>

1:11:16.583 --> 1:11:18.750
<i>You hate it, don't you?</i>

1:11:18.833 --> 1:11:19.833
<i>[Vesemir] I…</i>

1:11:21.166 --> 1:11:24.333
<i>I was just weighing whether you'd done</i>
<i>my dashing looks justice.</i>

1:11:24.416 --> 1:11:27.666
<i>[laughs] Oh, gods. You frightened me.</i>

1:11:27.750 --> 1:11:30.583
<i>Such a look in your eyes.</i>
<i>So crestfallen and…</i>

1:11:31.166 --> 1:11:32.375
<i>It's perfect, Illyana.</i>

1:11:33.458 --> 1:11:34.500
<i>Flawless.</i>

1:11:45.750 --> 1:11:47.666
<i>Don't dally. I'm thirsty.</i>

1:11:49.666 --> 1:11:51.250
<i>Mama! Make Bojan stop!</i>

1:11:51.333 --> 1:11:53.250
<i>He's run away with my jacks!</i>

1:11:54.791 --> 1:11:57.708
<i>What's wrong, Papa?</i>
<i>You're making the sad face.</i>

1:11:58.291 --> 1:11:59.541
<i>No, no…</i>

1:12:00.250 --> 1:12:01.208
<i>This is wrong.</i>

1:12:01.291 --> 1:12:03.833
<i>Enough mind games, Kitsu.</i>
<i>No more fantasies.</i>

1:12:03.916 --> 1:12:05.916
<i>[wind gusting]</i>

1:12:06.541 --> 1:12:09.333
<i>But you swore</i>
<i>you'd care for me, didn't you?</i>

1:12:10.333 --> 1:12:11.500
<i>That you'd protect me.</i>

1:12:12.541 --> 1:12:13.916
<i>You're not real.</i>

1:12:14.000 --> 1:12:17.208
<i>Truth is no illusion.</i>
<i>There's no escaping it.</i>

1:12:17.750 --> 1:12:19.458
<i>[gasps] Get away from me!</i>

1:12:20.041 --> 1:12:22.125
<i>You left me here, darling.</i>

1:12:22.208 --> 1:12:25.041
<i>Stranded in hopes and dreams abandoned.</i>

1:12:25.125 --> 1:12:27.833
<i>And now you're trying to leave me again.</i>

1:12:27.916 --> 1:12:30.708
<i>Only this time, I won't be buried</i>

1:12:30.791 --> 1:12:33.083
<i>-in dresses and courts and titles.</i>
<i>-[thunder rumbling]</i>

1:12:33.166 --> 1:12:36.666
<i>I'll be as you are. Lost and alone.</i>

1:12:36.750 --> 1:12:38.791
<i>Unloved!</i>

1:12:38.875 --> 1:12:40.958
<i>No, Illyana. I love you.</i>

1:12:41.041 --> 1:12:42.458
<i>Coin's your real lover.</i>

1:12:43.416 --> 1:12:46.250
<i>More of her</i>
<i>to pluck out there, isn't there?</i>

1:12:46.750 --> 1:12:47.708
<i>Stop it.</i>

1:12:47.791 --> 1:12:50.375
<i>We can be</i>
<i>whatever we imagine here, Vesemir.</i>

1:12:50.458 --> 1:12:51.750
<i>We can be rich.</i>

1:12:51.833 --> 1:12:57.541
<i>-Together. Here, time is nothing.</i>
<i>-[thunder rumbling]</i>

1:12:58.708 --> 1:13:00.541
<i>Out there, I can save her.</i>

1:13:01.458 --> 1:13:02.791
<i>That's worth more.</i>

1:13:02.875 --> 1:13:04.208
<i>Now, out of my head.</i>

1:13:11.750 --> 1:13:14.125
<i>[epic music playing]</i>

1:13:20.916 --> 1:13:21.916
<i>[yells]</i>

1:13:39.291 --> 1:13:41.541
<i>[Tetra] I know you never asked for this.</i>

1:13:42.708 --> 1:13:44.041
<i>You were only a child.</i>

1:13:44.541 --> 1:13:46.083
<i>How were you to know?</i>

1:13:48.375 --> 1:13:49.583
<i>[roars]</i>

1:13:56.791 --> 1:13:57.625
<i>[Kitsu hisses]</i>

1:13:59.500 --> 1:14:00.791
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Vesemir!</i>

1:14:01.541 --> 1:14:02.625
<i>Stay back!</i>

1:14:24.833 --> 1:14:25.833
<i>[yells]</i>

1:14:37.333 --> 1:14:39.291
<i>You come at me with magic tricks?</i>

1:14:49.166 --> 1:14:51.250
<i>[yelling]</i>

1:14:55.166 --> 1:14:56.666
<i>[music slows]</i>

1:15:03.500 --> 1:15:04.875
<i>[Kitsu grunts]</i>

1:15:12.166 --> 1:15:13.208
<i>[gasps]</i>

1:15:18.000 --> 1:15:19.666
<i>Oh, no… [gasps]</i>

1:15:21.208 --> 1:15:22.958
<i>No! No!</i>

1:15:23.625 --> 1:15:24.958
<i>No, no, no, no!</i>

1:15:25.625 --> 1:15:26.541
<i>[panting]</i>

1:15:27.250 --> 1:15:28.375
<i>[Lady Zerbst] Vesemir.</i>

1:15:30.583 --> 1:15:31.416
<i>[Vesemir] Oh.</i>

1:15:33.500 --> 1:15:34.458
<i>This…</i>

1:15:35.291 --> 1:15:36.416
<i>this isn't real.</i>

1:15:39.666 --> 1:15:42.500
<i>I didn't know much about witchers</i>
<i>when I was young.</i>

1:15:42.583 --> 1:15:45.625
<i>I didn't know</i>
<i>you could smell better, hear better.</i>

1:15:46.333 --> 1:15:49.083
<i>I didn't know that the witcher</i>
<i>sensed me in the cupboard,</i>

1:15:49.166 --> 1:15:51.166
<i>trembling, barely breathing,</i>

1:15:51.250 --> 1:15:54.083
<i>watching as he drove his sword</i>
<i>through my mother.</i>

1:15:54.583 --> 1:15:58.250
<i>The silly sorceress</i>
<i>who'd crossed a gullible priest.</i>

1:15:59.250 --> 1:16:01.250
<i>Monsters to kill monsters.</i>

1:16:02.041 --> 1:16:03.791
<i>[gurgling]</i>

1:16:06.375 --> 1:16:07.333
<i>Aye…</i>

1:16:13.000 --> 1:16:13.875
<i>So…</i>

1:16:17.666 --> 1:16:18.500
<i>[grunts]</i>

1:16:22.375 --> 1:16:23.791
<i>Take her and go.</i>

1:16:25.625 --> 1:16:27.916
<i>Sven? The others?</i>

1:16:29.500 --> 1:16:30.333
<i>Dead.</i>

1:16:31.583 --> 1:16:33.000
<i>All my boys.</i>

1:16:33.791 --> 1:16:35.833
<i>-Save you.</i>
<i>-[Lady Zerbst] The young ones…</i>

1:16:36.708 --> 1:16:38.541
<i>-escaped.</i>
<i>-[Vesemir chuckles]</i>

1:16:39.166 --> 1:16:40.291
<i>Keep your strength.</i>

1:16:42.541 --> 1:16:44.625
<i>They're your boys now, young fella.</i>

1:16:45.208 --> 1:16:46.375
<i>Make 'em witchers.</i>

1:16:46.875 --> 1:16:47.958
<i>Make 'em…</i>

1:16:48.541 --> 1:16:49.791
<i>somethin' more.</i>

1:16:52.375 --> 1:16:54.125
<i>To better men.</i>

1:16:58.583 --> 1:17:00.583
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

1:17:12.375 --> 1:17:15.333
<i>She didn't ask for this.</i>

1:17:39.416 --> 1:17:41.416
<i>[somber music continues]</i>

1:18:05.875 --> 1:18:07.666
<i>-[ice cracking]</i>
<i>-Where are we?</i>

1:18:26.166 --> 1:18:27.666
<i>Beautiful. [sighs]</i>

1:18:29.083 --> 1:18:31.666
<i>It doesn't seem… real.</i>

1:18:38.000 --> 1:18:39.000
<i>[crying]</i>

1:18:41.250 --> 1:18:42.500
<i>[sobbing]</i>

1:18:59.291 --> 1:19:00.583
<i>[grunts]</i>

1:19:02.166 --> 1:19:03.250
<i>Huh?</i>

1:19:05.458 --> 1:19:07.875
<i>-Do we even know where we're going?</i>
<i>-[horse neighs]</i>

1:19:18.791 --> 1:19:21.666
<i>This is the last time</i>
<i>I allow any of you to ever hesitate.</i>

1:19:22.333 --> 1:19:23.416
<i>Decide.</i>

1:19:24.916 --> 1:19:26.291
<i>But they hate us.</i>

1:19:27.625 --> 1:19:29.250
<i>There'll always be another monster…</i>

1:19:29.333 --> 1:19:30.333
<i>Geralt.</i>

1:19:37.166 --> 1:19:39.166
<i>[epic music playing]</i>

1:20:45.083 --> 1:20:48.541
<i>[woman] </i>♪ There once was a lord ♪

1:20:49.208 --> 1:20:53.458
<i>♪ In dark woods ♪</i>

1:20:53.958 --> 1:20:57.875
<i>♪ Wearing a strange ♪</i>

1:20:57.958 --> 1:21:03.041
<i>♪ Silver band ♪</i>

1:21:03.791 --> 1:21:07.833
<i>♪ Around ♪</i>

1:21:07.916 --> 1:21:11.666
<i>♪ His hand ♪</i>

1:21:13.166 --> 1:21:17.625
<i>♪ For the bandit also ♪</i>

1:21:17.708 --> 1:21:24.708
<i>♪ Feared ♪</i>

1:21:25.791 --> 1:21:32.416
<i>♪ Monsters</i> ♪

1:21:33.541 --> 1:21:40.416
<i>♪ Monsters</i> ♪
